(6, 1, 'Web programmer di PT Dynapack', 'PT DYNAPACK INDONESIA (DYNAPLAST)', '<p>The leading and largest rigid plastic packaging company in Indonesia is looking for highly qualified professionals.&nbsp; We need people who are self-motivated and team players, good in following skills of which are English both oral and written, communication and interpersonal, and computer skills, to join us in a competitive environment for the following position :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WEB APPLICATION PROGRAMMER (Code : IT)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fresh Graduate or max. 2 year working experience</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor Degree in Computer Science/ Information Technology with min. GPA 3.50 from a reputable university</li>\r\n	<li>Required knowledge and skill in Programming: <em>PHP, Javascript, MySQL, Joomla, HTML, DTHML, CSS, Desktop Application(C#)</em></li>\r\n	<li>Have strong logic, algorithm, and analytical thinking</li>\r\n	<li>Good leadership skill, strong project management skill, good communication skill, and good developing people skill</li>\r\n	<li>Will be located in Lippo Karawaci, Tangerang.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Please submit your application letter with a recent passport size photograph and comprehensive resume, academic transcript and quote the position code on the top left envelope soon to:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Corporate HR</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PT Dyna</strong><strong>pack Indonesia</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dynaplast Tower 9-10th Floor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jl. MH. Thamrin No. 1</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lippo Karawaci &ndash; Tangerang 15811</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>or </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:eveline.hartono@dynapackasia.com\"><strong>eveline.hartono@dynapackasia.com</strong></a> not later than <strong>November 09, 2015</strong>.</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2015-11-20', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-11-30 00:00:00', NULL, NU