(10, 1, 'Open recruitment at Sinar Mas Group', 'PT INDAH KIAT PULP and PAPER Tbk (SINAR MAS)', '<p>APP (Asia Pulp and Paper Products), Sinar Mas Group is one of the world&rsquo;s leading pulp and paper companies. With current combined pulp, paper and packaging grades capacity of over 7 million tonnes in Indonesia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>APP currently has multi-location manufacturing facilities in Indonesia and markets its products in more than 65 countries on six continents. APP produces bleached hardwood pulp and a wide range of paper and packaging products. The range extends from commodity-grade base paper to value added art paper that includes cast coat paper, tissue, specialty papers, stationery, office product, and carbonless paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We challenge you to join our team in Indah Kiat Pulp &amp; Paper Tangerang as :</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ACCOUNTING STAFF</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Male/Female, max 30 years old</li>\r\n	<li>S1 degree majoring Accounting with GPA 3,00 (Scale 4)</li>\r\n	<li>Having 1 &ndash; 2 years experience, fresh graduate are welcome</li>\r\n	<li>Ready to avertime work, hard worker, ready to work under pressure, good working attitude</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent in Microsoft Office (excel, word &amp; power point)</li>\r\n	<li>Fluency in English is a must and Mandarin will be an advantage</li>\r\n	<li>Willing to be located in Serpong, Tangerang</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IT SUPPORT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Male/Female, max 30 years old</li>\r\n	<li>S1 or D3 degree from Computer Engineering/Related Education with GPA 3,00 (scale 4)</li>\r\n	<li>Having 1 year experience in Manufacturing System Analyst/Programming (Fresh Graduate Welcome)</li>\r\n	<li>Good Knowledge in SAP/Programming/Web/Database/Analysis System</li>\r\n	<li>Strong analytical, statistical knowledge and problem solving skills, having visual studio. NET (vb.NET/C#) untuk Web (ASP.NET), VB 6, html, css, XML and javascript ability.</li>\r\n	<li>Hard Worker, ready to work