(14, 1, 'Terbuka Peluang di Tokopedia', 'TOKOPEDIA', '<p><strong>SOFTWARE ENGINEER</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Develop new features according to roadmap</li>\r\n	<li>Monitor bug report and execute bug fixing</li>\r\n	<li>Develop back-end for operational efficiency</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree. Maximum 28 years of age.</li>\r\n	<li>Have passion to build products that are useful to many people.</li>\r\n	<li>Interested in following updates on web technology.</li>\r\n	<li>Creative and able to work on deadline.</li>\r\n	<li>Communicative and able to work in team.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Software Test Engineer </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Create automation system to ensure that the products developed by the company meet the quality standards and requirements.</li>\r\n	<li>Create documentations for the test plans and test cases.</li>\r\n	<li>Set the estimated processing time and ensure that all product tests can be finished on time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Experienced in Perl, and /or Python programming language.</li>\r\n	<li>Able to conduct task and responsibility according to deadline.</li>\r\n	<li>Familiar with testing methodology and tools.</li>\r\n	<li>Have experience in user level test automation.</li>\r\n	<li>High analyzing skill and attention to details.</li>\r\n	<li>Deep understanding of testing during all parts of the software life cycle.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Business Merchant Development &ndash; Retention</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Responsible for retain&nbsp;merchant accounts both via social media and face-to-face.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Perform the strategic, tactical and support functions in strengthening relationships within the merchant segment.</li>\r\n	<li>Primary responsibility in retain current merchants.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain comunity relations with Tokopedia&#39;s merchant across Indonesia</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Requirements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Detail oriented team player with good planning and problem solving skills whom is willing to go the extra mile.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Strong analytical and communication skill.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sense of urgency for incident resolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ability to multi-task in a fast paced environment with minimal direction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Fluent in english&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Data Analyst</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Gather and compile data from various sources in order to observe the company&#39;s performance and direct its business advancement.</li>\r\n	<li>Develop business campaign.</li>\r\n	<li>Create the company, division, and individual performance indicator.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bachelor degree in Statistic, Computer Science, Information Technology or related fileds.</li>\r\n	<li>Have a good knowledge of warehouse data center.</li>\r\n	<li>Have understanding in business process and user requirement management.</li>\r\n	<li>Good analytical and conceptual thinking skills, creative and innovative.</li>\r\n	<li>Comfortable multi-tasking in a aggressive, competitive, environment, and working under pressure.</li>\r\n	<li>Self-motivated and a team player at the same time.</li>\r\n	<li>Good personality, hardworking, trustworthy, keen to learn and discipline.</li>\r\n	<li>Detail oriented and posses decent communication skill.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Graphic Designer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Enhance the visual identity the Tokopedia website</li>\r\n	<li>Create advertisements banners for Tokopedia to be displayed online and offline.</li>\r\n	<li>Creative flair, originality and a strong visual sense</li>\r\n	<li>Strong computer skills.</li>\r\n	<li>Confidence, to present and explain ideas.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>Requirement:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Should know how to use Photoshop, Illustrator and Flash.</li>\r\n	<li>Graphic design education is a plus.</li>\r\n	<li>Writing skill (advertorials, catalogs, media releases, new articles).</li>\r\n	<li>Great sense of urgency</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>*SHOULD YOU BE INTERESTED IN JOINING US, PLEASE SEND YOUR CV&amp;PORTFOLIO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Administrator</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hot product updating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Planning category update.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Catalog updating (photo, specifications, and market price).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Monitoring content (product and category).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Moderating shops and products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor&rsquo;s degree from all departments, maximum 26 years old.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Posses good product knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Up to date with e-commerce trends.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Focus on detail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Familiar with newest technology and social media platforms (blog, Facebook, Twitter, G+, etc).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Have good copywriting sense to write product description.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proficient in Microsoft Office.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Able to operate basic Adobe Photoshop is a plus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Submit your CV to </strong><a href=\"http://www.tokopedia.com/careers\"><strong>www.tokopedia.com/careers</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2015-12-02', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-23 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Software Engineer, Business Merchant Development, Graphic Designer, dll.', 0),
(13, 1, 'Mau Bergabung bersama Sinar Mas Group?', 'PT INDAH KIAT PULP and PAPER Tbk (SINAR MAS)', '<p>APP (Asia Pulp and Paper Products), Sinar Mas Group is one of the world&rsquo;s leading pulp and paper companies. With current combined pulp, paper and packaging grades capacity of over 7 million tonnes in Indonesia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>APP currently has multi-location manufacturing facilities in Indonesia and markets its products in more than 65 countries on six continents. APP produces bleached hardwood pulp and a wide range of paper and packaging products. The range extends from commodity-grade base paper to value added art paper that includes cast coat paper, tissue, specialty papers, stationery, office product, and carbonless paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We challenge you to join our team in Indah Kiat Pulp &amp; Paper Tangerang as :</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ACCOUNTING STAFF</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Male/Female, max 30 years old</li>\r\n	<li>S1 degree majoring Accounting with GPA 3,00 (Scale 4)</li>\r\n	<li>Having 1 &ndash; 2 years experience, fresh graduate are welcome</li>\r\n	<li>Ready to avertime work, hard worker, ready to work under pressure, good working attitude</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent in Microsoft Office (excel, word &amp; power point)</li>\r\n	<li>Fluency in English is a must and Mandarin will be an advantage</li>\r\n	<li>Willing to be located in Serpong, Tangerang</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IT SUPPORT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Male/Female, max 30 years old</li>\r\n	<li>S1 or D3 degree from Computer Engineering/Related Education with GPA 3,00 (scale 4)</li>\r\n	<li>Having 1 year experience in Manufacturing System Analyst/Programming (Fresh Graduate Welcome)</li>\r\n	<li>Good Knowledge in SAP/Programming/Web/Database/Analysis System</li>\r\n	<li>Strong analytical, statistical knowledge and problem solving skills, having visual studio. NET (vb.NET/C#) untuk Web (ASP.NET), VB 6, html, css, XML and javascript ability.</li>\r\n	<li>Hard Worker, ready to work under pressure, good working attitude, strong leadership and having a good communication skills.</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent in Microsoft Office (excel, word &amp; power point)</li>\r\n	<li>Fluency in English is a must and Mandarin will be an advantage</li>\r\n	<li>Willing to be located in Serpong, Tangerang</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Please send your complete resume to the address bellow :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PT INDAH KIAT PULP and PAPER Tbk &ndash; Tangerang Mill</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jl. Raya Serpong Km. 8 &ndash; 15310</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Or please send your application to : <a href=\"mailto:Theresia_titirani@app.co.id\"><strong>Theresia_titirani@app.co.id</strong></a></p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, '2015-12-02', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-15 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Accounting Staff, IT Support', 0),
(15, 1, 'Kerja di Perusahaan Farmasi, Why Not?', 'PT KALBE FARMA, TBK', '<p><strong>PT KALBE FARMA, TBK</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saat ini sedang membuka kesempatan kerja untuk posisi :</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Android Programmer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>dengan kualifikasi :<br />\r\n1. Usia maksimal 26 tahun<br />\r\n2. Pendidikan min. S1 Teknik Informatika dengan IPK min. 3,0<br />\r\n3. Menguasai Android, Java, SQL, ASP.net<br />\r\n4. Bersedia ditempatkan di Cempaka Putih<br />\r\n5. Tersedia 2 posisi tetap<br />\r\n6. Fresh graduate are welcome to apply<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBagi yang berminat, bisa mengirimkan CV ke email <a href=\"mailto:kalbe.karir@kalbe.co.id\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>kalbe.karir@kalbe.co.id</strong></a></p>\r\n', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2015-12-02', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-15 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Android Programmer ', 0),
