(17, 1, 'Menjadi Bagian Inovasi Teknologi bersama BCA', 'PT BANK CENTRAL ASIA, TBK (BCA)', '<p><strong>MT IT (Management Trainee)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dalam program ini, para peserta akan mengikuti training penuh waktu selama 4 bulan, dan kemudian akan mengikuti on the job training selama 1.5 bulan di Divisi IT di BCA. Peserta yang lulus seluruh rangkaian training diatas, akan magang, dan nantinya akan ditempatkan sebagai karyawan tetap di Divisi IT, BCA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Persyaratan :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lulusan S1 dengan IPK minimal 3,00 (Strata 1) dan 3,25 (Strata 2)</li>\r\n	<li>Usia maks. 25 tahun (Strata 1) dan 27 tahun (Strata 2)</li>\r\n	<li>Memiliki latar belakang pendidikan atau pekerjaan di bidang computer</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Memiliki logika dan kemampuan analisa yang kuat</li>\r\n	<li>Dapat bekerja secara individu maupun di dalam tim</li>\r\n	<li>Memiliki kemampuan komunikasi dan hubungan interpersonal yang baik</li>\r\n	<li>Proaktif, kreatif, dan berintegritas tinggi</li>\r\n	<li>Bersedia menjalani ikatan dinas setelah pendidikan</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Informasi lebih lanjut <a href=\"http://www.karir.bca.co.id/\">: <strong>karir.bca.co.id</strong></a></p>\r\n', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2015-12-07', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-18 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'MT IT (Management Trainee)', 0),
(18, 1, 'Dynapack Looks for Analyst', 'PT. Dynapack Indonesia', '<p>The leading and largest rigid plastic packaging company in Indonesia is looking for highly qualified professionals.&nbsp; We need people who are self-motivated and team players, good in following skills of which are English both oral and written, communication and interpersonal, and computer skills, to join us in a competitive environment for the following position :</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Business Analyst (Code : BA)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications :</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Bachelor Degree (S1) with min. GPA 3.00 (Finance/Economic Management/Accounting/ Business Finance)</li>\r\n	<li>For Fresh Graduate</li>\r\n	<li>Fluent in English</li>\r\n	<li>Computer literate</li>\r\n	<li>Must be a self starter, independent, and good analytical skill</li>\r\n	<li>Good interpersonal skill and attitude</li>\r\n	<li>Willing to be located in Lippo Karawaci, Tangerang</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Please submit your application letter, comprehensive resume, with a recent photograph (size of 3x4) and quote the position code on the top left envelope to:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Corporate HR </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PT Dyn</strong><strong>apack Indonesia</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dynaplast Tower 9-10th Floor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jl. MH Thamrin No. 1</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lippo Karawaci, Tangerang 15811</strong><br />\r\n<em>Or</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:recruitment@dynapackasia.com\"><strong>recruitment@dynapackasia.com</strong></a> not later than<strong> December 18, 2015.</strong></p>\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2015-12-07', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-18 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Business Analyst (Code : BA)', 0),
(19, 1, 'TAKASAGO Open Recruitment', 'TAKASAGO INTERNATIONAL (SINGAPORE) PTE LTD', '<p>TAKASAGO INTERNATIONAL (SINGAPORE) PTE LTD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>INDONESIA REPRESENTATIVE OFFICE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Company Description:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a leading manufacturer of flavours and fragrances. We believe in seeking to define, refine and recreate the very essence of taste and smell, the most elusive of our senses and the most illusory. It is a never-ending quest that is the basis of our corporate philosophy and foundation and, most importantly, our contribution to society based on technology.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To support our business expansion and growth in the Asia Pacific region, we are seeking highly motivated individual to join us for the position of:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Finance and Admin</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>General administration&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Preparing payment</li>\r\n	<li>Key in all voucher to accounting system</li>\r\n	<li>Daily work in finance and accounting&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Female, at 22 &ndash; 25 years old.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Have initiative and hardworking personality</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Fluently speak in English both oral and written</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. S1 degree in accounting</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Market Research &amp; Regulatory Staff</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CIMR (Consumer Insight &amp; Market Research): prepare research documentation for a consumer test.</li>\r\n	<li>Regulatory: preparing supporting document for halal certification.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Female at maximum 25 years old</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. S1 degree</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Active and creative</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Able to work under pressure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Familiar with MS Office program</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Fluently speak in English both oral and written</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Has high passionate in administration work</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are interested in the above position and your profile corresponds to the above requirements, you are invited to apply by sending a detailed resume, stating current and expected salaries to :</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:career_id@takasago.com\"><strong>career_id@takasago.com</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2015-12-07', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-18 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Finance, Admin, Market Research & Regulatory Staff ', 0);
