(27, 1, 'Peluang Kerja  di Perusahaan Multi International SML ', 'PT SML INDONESIA PRIVATE', '<p>PT SML INDONESIA PRIVATE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A Multi International company is seeking suitables candidates for the following positions for our factory located in Serpong Tangerang.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ASSISTANT TO PRODUCTION MANAGER<br />\r\nRequirements :<br />\r\n- Minimum D3<br />\r\n- Maximum 30 years old<br />\r\n- Profiency in MS Office<br />\r\n- Fluent in Bahasa, English &amp; Mandarin (Must)<br />\r\n- Multi-tasking handling<br />\r\n- Strong analytical &amp; problem solving, decision making skill<br />\r\n- Work independent<br />\r\n- Willing to work overtime</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IT OFFICER<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n- Minimum S1 Any Major<br />\r\n- Maximum 30 years old<br />\r\n- Experience in IT min 2 years, as Programmer<br />\r\n- Good Visual Basic and C++ (Must)<br />\r\n- LAN and WAN<br />\r\n- Fluent in English<br />\r\n- Honesty, responsibility<br />\r\n- Male<br />\r\n- Fresh Grads are welcome<br />\r\n- We expect&nbsp; result&nbsp; instead of education background and therefore we challenges any graduates<br />\r\n- Able to work independent&nbsp; with a minimum of supervision</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FINANCE &amp; ACCOUNTING STAFF<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n- Female, max 25 years old<br />\r\n- Education min Senior High School<br />\r\n- Min 1 year&nbsp; experience in making Faktur Pajak PPN and other administration jobs<br />\r\n- Familiar with MS Office application<br />\r\n- Good interpersonal communication, adaptive, proactive and self motivated</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SALES<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n- Minimum 1 years sales experience preferable from trave industry<br />\r\n- Fluent in English and computer literate<br />\r\n- Attractive, aggressive and good communication skill</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAll must be place in Serpong, Tangerang Selatan<br />\r\nIf you are confident that you fit our qualifications, we would like to have a further conversation with you.<br />\r\nPlease send your CV, recent photograph to :<br />\r\nIndonesia@sml.com / purnamas@sml.com<br />\r\nOr<br />\r\nHRD Manager<br />\r\nKomp. Pergudangan Multiguna Blok B1/7 Jl. MH. Thamrin KM 7 Kel. Pakualam Kec. Serpong Utara Kota Tangerang Selatan - Banten</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2016-01-05', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Production Manager Assistant, Finance, IT Officer, Sales', 0),
(36, 1, 'Peluang Karir bersama KAWAN LAMA GROUP', 'KAWAN LAMA GROUP', '<p><strong>1. Senior Merchandiser</strong><br />\r\nResponsibilities :<br />\r\n- Monitoring achievement of sales target and inventory/stock every month<br />\r\n- Responsible for the promotion of department&#39;s products and review vendor list</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications :<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree in any major<br />\r\n- Have experience min. 4 years as Buyer/Merchandiser, preferably in retail business/buying agent/eCommerce<br />\r\n- Willing to travel<br />\r\n- Fluent in English (able to speak Mandarin is an advantage)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. E-Commerce Developer</strong><br />\r\nResponsibilities :<br />\r\n- Improve and manage E-commerce platform (ie. Magento, Prestashop)<br />\r\n- Conduct performance tuning and customization of E-commerce Solution platform<br />\r\n- Architect and built custom modules or other new functionality using object oriented PHP and E-commerce Solution APIs<br />\r\n- Providing regular development progress feedback and consistently meet the project deadlines<br />\r\n- Monitor day to day activities of the technical delivery team<br />\r\n- Provide regular project status reports to stakeholders and IT management<br />\r\n- Participate in ad-hoc IT/non IT related business project when necessary</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications :<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree in Information Technology, Science &amp; Technology, Commerce or equivalent<br />\r\n- Have experience min. 4 years in E-commerce, Linux, PHP development or the related field<br />\r\n- Understanding JSON, JavaScript while XML is advantage<br />\r\n- Strong skill with network programming in PHP</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Digital Marketing &amp; Promotion Strategist</strong><br />\r\nResponsibilities :<br />\r\n- Responsible for strategy and execution for website content marketing<br />\r\n- Implementation of effective promotional campaigns<br />\r\n- Create and developing monthly promotion for E-commerce<br />\r\n- Responsible for digital advertising of the website<br />\r\n- Provide financial projection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications :<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree in any major<br />\r\n- Have experience min. 3 years in E-marketing, Marketing Promotion in Ecommerce/Digital industry<br />\r\n- Experd knowledge about various marketing strategies, affiliate marketing, and online campaign management</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Call Center Team Leader</strong><br />\r\nResponsibilities :<br />\r\n- Handle and follow up the priority customer&#39;s complaint by phone<br />\r\n- Maintain good relationship with customer database, especially member<br />\r\n- Managing a team of call center agents, increasing performance and team capabilities</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications :<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree in any field<br />\r\n- Have experience min. 1 year as Call Center Team Leader<br />\r\n- Willing to work in shift time and also on public holiday</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. IT Networking Officer</strong><br />\r\nResponsibilities :<br />\r\n- Implementing, maintaining, monitoring network security<br />\r\n- Installing, maintaining and supporting computer communication networks within the office<br />\r\n- Handle troubleshooting hardware/software, PC and server</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications :<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree in Information Technology/Computer Science or equivalent<br />\r\n- Have experience min. 2 years as IT Networking<br />\r\n- Understanding the basic fundamentals on designing network infrastructures and configuring network devices<br />\r\n- Good knowledge of network security (firewall), network protocol, network device (routers and switches), operating system<br />\r\n- Able to configure and maintain email server, troubleshooting hardware and software</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6. Accounting Officer</strong><br />\r\nResponsibilities :<br />\r\nHandle daily administrative and financial task, prepares financial/accounting reports (balance sheet, profit &amp; loss, cash flow, etc.)<br />\r\nQualifications :<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree in Accounting or equivalent<br />\r\n- Have experience min. 1 year as Finance/Accounting/Account Receivable/Account Payable<br />\r\n- Computer literate</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>7. Tax Officer</strong><br />\r\nResponsibilities:<br />\r\n- Prepare monthly tax reporting, including running the electronic tax reporting program (named E-SPT)<br />\r\n- Reconcile all taxes between book and supporting documents on monthly basis<br />\r\n- Prepare/review tax returns (reporting), other accounting and Tax related function</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications :<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree in Economics, Finance/Accountancy/Banking or equivalent<br />\r\n- Have experience min. 2 years in the related field<br />\r\n- Good knowledge in taxation, having certificate of &ldquo;Brevet A/B&rdquo;<br />\r\n- Proficient MS Application skills with some knowledge in SAP<br />\r\n- Familiar with Microsoft Office sofware: word, excell, power point, internet, acc software</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>8. Traffic Import Officer</strong><br />\r\nResponsibilities :<br />\r\n- Responsible for all aspects of import shipments and monitoring document import<br />\r\n- Controlling payment and import cost<br />\r\n- Maintaining a good relationship with forwarder, shipping company and related government department</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications :<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree in any major<br />\r\n- Have experience min. 1 year in the related field<br />\r\n- Understanding import and customs regulation<br />\r\n- Fluent in English (able to speak Mandarin is an advantage)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>9. Sales Data Analyst</strong><br />\r\nResponsibilities:<br />\r\n- Create, monitor, and analyze daily, weekly, and monthly data of regional sales report</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualifications:<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree in Economics, Engineering, Business Management, or equivalent<br />\r\n- Have experience min. 1 year as Data Analyst.<br />\r\n- Interest in administrative duties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Please kindly send your resume &amp; photograph to : indah.mekar@kawanlamaretail.com </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>or by post to HRD Kawan Lama Group, Kawan Lama Building 6th floor, Jl. Puri Kencana No 1. Kembangan. Jakarta Barat 11610</strong></p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2016-01-19', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-31 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Senior Merchandiser, E-commerce developer, Accounting Officer, etc.', 0),
(31, 1, 'Montis Boga Undang yang Berjiwa Energik', 'PT MONTIS BOGA', '<p>PT Montis Boga, produsen makanan yang berkantor pusat di Serpong, Tangerang, mengundang<br />\r\nAnda yang berjiwa enerjik untuk bergabung bersama kami untuk posisi sebagai berikut:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.MARKETING (MKT)<br />\r\n2.MERCHANDISER (MDR)<br />\r\n3.ADMINISTRATOR (ADM)<br />\r\n4.ACCOUNTING (ACC)<br />\r\n5. ASSISTANT PRODUCTION (APR)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kualifikasi Umum :<br />\r\n- Usia maksimum 30 tahun untuk semua posisi<br />\r\n- Memiliki kendaraan sendiri dan SIM (MKT, MDR)<br />\r\n- Mampu mengoperasikan MS Office (ADM, ACC)<br />\r\n- Jurusan D3/S1 akuntansi (ACC)<br />\r\n- Diutamakan yang memiliki pengalaman kerja sekurangnya 3 tahun untuk posisi MKT,<br />\r\nMDR, APR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Surat lamaran disertai foto, CV, dan fotokopi ijasah terakhir agar dikirimkan ke email:<br />\r\ninfo@montis.co.id selambat-lambatnya tanggal 15 Januari 2016.</p>\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2016-01-11', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'MARKETING, MERCHANDISER, ADMINISTRATOR, ACCOUNTING, ASSISTANT PRODUCTION', 0),
(30, 1, 'Bergabung bersama Dynapack', 'PT DYNAPACK INDONESIA (DYNAPLAST)', '<p>The leading and largest rigid plastic packaging company in Indonesia is looking for highly qualified professionals. We have 10 companies within the DYNAPACK ASIA group, across 5 countries (Indonesia, Thailand, Vietnam, Malaysia, and China), with a total of 27 manufacturing plants. We need people who are self-motivated and team players, good in following skills of which are English both oral and written, communication and interpersonal, and computer skills, to join us in a competitive environment for the following position :</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nBUSINESS ANALYST (Code : BA)<br />\r\nQualifications :<br />\r\n1. Bachelor Degree (S1) with min. GPA 3.00 (Finance/Economic Management/Accounting/ Business Finance)<br />\r\n2. For Fresh Graduate<br />\r\n3. Fluent in English<br />\r\n4. Computer literate<br />\r\n5. Must be a self starter, independent, and good analytical skill<br />\r\n6. Good interpersonal skill and attitude<br />\r\n7. Willing to be located in Lippo Karawaci, Tangerang</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nFINANCE ADMIN (Code : Fin)<br />\r\nQualifications :<br />\r\n1. Bachelor Degree (S1) with min. GPA 3.00 in Accounting with min. GPA is 3.00<br />\r\n2. Fresh graduate or 1 year experience in related field,<br />\r\n3. Required skill in English (speaking and writing)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Understand for making accounting ledger<br />\r\n5. Able to operat Ms. Office,<br />\r\n6. Responsibility, thorough, deft,<br />\r\n7. Will be located in Lippo Karawaci, Tangerang.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please submit your application letter with a recent passport size photograph and comprehensive resume, and quote the position code on the top left envelope :</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nCorporate HR<br />\r\nPT Dynaplast<br />\r\nDynaplast Tower 9-10th Floor<br />\r\nJl. MH. Thamrin No. 1<br />\r\nLippo Karawaci &ndash; Tangerang 15811<br />\r\nor<br />\r\neveline.hartono@dynapackasia.com not later than Januari 18, 2016.</p>\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2016-01-08', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-18 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Business Analyst (Code : BA), FINANCE ADMIN (Code : Fin)', 0),
(37, 1, 'Are You Challenged to be Creative Web Developer?', 'PT AMALAN INTERNATIONAL INDONESIA', '<p>We are currently looking for a resourceful and creative<strong> WEB DEVELOPER/DESIGNER</strong> talent to continuously develop our website and add a designer touch throughout our digital communication.<br />\r\nOur mission at amalan is to assist people in regaining control of their finances. We advise our customers on ways to renegotiate their loans to a level they can afford. We are first to offer such service in Indonesia using a professional, attentive and customer focused approach, supported by cutting edge technology.<br />\r\nAs <strong>WEB DEVELOPER/DESIGNER</strong> you will contribute toward shaping amalan&#39;s website and keep the technology relevant with our customer focused solution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br />\r\n- Design, code and modify websites and blogs, from layout to function and according to amalan&#39;s specifications and message attentive, customer focused and professional<br />\r\n- Strive to create visually appealing sites that feature userfriendly design and clear navigation<br />\r\n- Work systematically on continuous improvements to ensure the website is relevant and up to date<br />\r\n- Ensure that website is compatible with other cloud based systems</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong><br />\r\n- Strong understanding of UI, crossbrowser compatibility, general web functions and standards<br />\r\n- Superb graphic design skills combined with experience in building websites<br />\r\n- Good understanding of programming language of HTML and Java experience with squarespace is definitely a plus but not a requirement<br />\r\n- Understanding of web security principles<br />\r\n- Fresh graduate from top school and/or up to 2 years relevant experience is encouraged to apply<br />\r\n- Fluent Bahasa Indonesia and good English<br />\r\n- This is a full time position</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is an exciting opportunity wi thin a small and dynamic team in a high growth startup led by an international group of experienced finance and startup veterans (for bios, please visit: amalan). It is a fun job for a highly motivated and creative person that learns quickly and likes a fast moving, challenging environment. We offer a startup environment with flat hierarchy that gives you ample space to develop yourself professionally and to apply your creativity. Starting salary and benefits are competitive with excellent growth perspective.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Please drop your job application to: http://www.amalan.org/joinus/2015/8/13/webdeveloperdesignerjakarta</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Office address:<br />\r\nPalma Tower, Lt. 20<br />\r\nJl R. A. Kartini II S/06 T. B. Simatupang<br />\r\nJakarta 12310<br />\r\nT: 021 5126 2526<br />\r\nwww.amalan.id</strong></p>\r\n', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-01-19', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-31 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Web Developer/Designer', 0),
