Move Subscriber, Data Migration, Change Priceplan, Voucher Activation)<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n- S1 in Engineering : Electrical Engineering or Information System preferably<br />\r\n- Fresh graduate/1 year working experience preferable in Telco industry<br />\r\n- Basic understanding of UNIX &amp; PL/SQL<br />\r\n- Basic understanding of Database<br />\r\n- Basic Understanding/Knowledge in Billing System, preferably in billing telco<br />\r\n- Problem solving<br />\r\n- Communication &amp; coordination<br />\r\n- Team Work<br />\r\n- Attention to Detail<br />\r\n- Customer Orientation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Engineer IT Settlements<br />\r\nJob Roles:<br />\r\n- Build, deliver and support the Settlement systems which are being used for financial settlement and revenue accounting purposes.<br />\r\n- Developing the solutions which processes the data from various sources and generate the reports and detail data<br />\r\n- Application support for the technical issues<br />\r\n- Application support for ad-hoc requirements<br />\r\n- Liaise with requirement managers, business users, designers, vendors to be able to deliver comprehensive solution<br />\r\n- Review the application and output data to ensure the quality of solution<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n- Degree in Computer Science/IT/Engineering, or equivalent years of experience.<br />\r\n- Minimum 3 years experience in development of Settlement/business-intelligence/data-warehousing/revenue-assurance area will be an advantage.<br />\r\n- Basic to intermediate knowledge in OSS source systems (Billing, CRM, ERP, card management etc).<br />\r\n- Basic to intermediate knowledge in Enterprise DBMS development (eg. Oracle PL/SQL) &amp; Unix Scripting.<br />\r\n- Basic to intermediate knowledge in ETL platform e.g. Data Stage/OWB/Ab-initio/other ETL tool.<br />\r\n- Basic to intermediate knowledge in Financial settlement, Business Intelligence &amp; data warehousing concepts, data and dimensional modeling, data quality principles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nKalau berminat bisa mengirimkan CV ke xlapp.diptyar@xl.co.id dengan subjek nama posisi yang dilamar.</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2016-01-27', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-21 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Engineer – Billing Development, Engineer – Touchpoint &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; Fulfillment, etc.', 0),
