(45, 1, 'Berkarir dari MT Social Media', 'TEMPO Group', '<p><strong>THE TEMPO GROUP - A DEDICATION TO QUALITY SINCE 1953</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>URGENTLY REQUIRED</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Group Tempo exist since 1953 as a company group which produce, selling and licensee from pharmaceutical, eutical, healthy care, cosmetic and consumer products such as: Hemaviton, Bodrexin, Bodrex, Neo Rheumacyl, Oskadon, Vidoran, Revlon, Estee Lauder, Clinique, Marina, My Baby, Claudia, Total Care, SOS, Pritho, Exclusive Barclay, Fraser &amp; Neave (F&amp;N), etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, to support our business growth and operation, The Tempo Group has vacancy for experience, higher education, young and professionals as:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Management Trainee - Social Media</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><u>Requirements </u></strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Male/Female, min. 21 years old</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor Degree, any major with IPK min. 3,00</li>\r\n	<li>Fresh Graduate / max. 1 year working experience in social media or related field</li>\r\n	<li>Able to attract and interact with targeted virtual communities and networks users on Social Media platform</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent consulting, writing, presentation and communication skills for developing content.</li>\r\n	<li>Preferably familiar with editing tools for photo/video/text/gif.</li>\r\n	<li>Demonstrable social networking experience and social analytics tools knowledge</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge of online marketing and good understanding of major marketing channels</li>\r\n	<li>Positive attitude, detail and customer oriented with good multitasking and organisational ability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Please send your detail resume, CV of digital experience, with photograph not later than two weeks after this advertisement to:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>THE TEMPO GROUP</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Email: </strong><strong><u>aza</u></strong><strong><u>@thetempogroup.com</u></strong></p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2016-02