(50, 1, 'Freshgrad Vacancy in Poperty Field', 'Letsmoveindonesia.com', '<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Fresh Graduate Vacancy</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>LetsMoveIndonesia</strong> is a free property comparison website where you can browse, sell or<br />\r\nrent private residences, offices or land. We will be officially live in February 2016.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">We are looking for an <strong>IT Designer</strong><br />\r\nJob Description:<br />\r\nHelp to maintain and update the website<br />\r\nDesign merchandise and promotional materials<br />\r\nDevelop brand awareness using social media &amp; other methods<br />\r\nHelp design, develop and launch new products</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />\r\nPassionate about design<br />\r\nHave a good understanding/desire to learn, how to use WordPress themes<br />\r\nAble to design promotion materials, office stationary, logos and merchandise<br />\r\nHave a good understanding of social media strategies<br />\r\nWant to be part of an exciting start up with limitless opportunities</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Send your CV to:Dwi@letsmoveindonesia.com</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">*Please note that this position is for a 3-month contract with the potential for extension<br />\r\nfor the right candidate.</span></p>\r\n', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-02-17', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-29 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'c17801a8ff47ac725dc8a91201bfaea04ac33867.png', 1, 'IT Designer', 0),
