(52, 1, 'ALLIANZ INDONESIA : Agency Strategic Development Officer / Supervisor (Fresh graduate welcome)', 'Allianz Indonesia', '<p><strong><u>Company Overview</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Allianz is one of the largest global providers of insurance and asset management. Asia Pacific is one of Allianz&#39;s three major growth regions. It is characterized by its rich diversity of cultures, languages and customs. Now, Allianz Indonesia presents in 46 cities with more than 90 service centers, supported by more than 16,000 agents with more than 1,200 employees and solid banking partners to serve our customer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><u>Why Join Us?</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are big multinational company from Germany and we provide a learn culture to employees which want to growth his/her capability and skill.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, to support our business growth, Allianz Indonesia is looking for:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Agency Strategic Development Officer / Supervisor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job description</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Execute project development and improvement in Agency Channel</li>\r\n	<li>Involve in Change management project</li>\r\n	<li>Act as internal couch or consultant</li>\r\n	<li>Control and Monitoring on-going project</li>\r\n	<li>Provide regular updates and performance report</li>\r\n	<li>Business Analysis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specific Requirement:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Education (Bachelor Degree)\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Information System, Computer Science and Computer System</li>\r\n		<li>Engineering (Computer / Telecommunication)</li>\r\n		<li>Technic or Engineering equivalent</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Project Management (Basic)</li>\r\n		<li>Business Process Improvement (Basic)</li>\r\n		<li>People Development / Coach (Basic)</li>\r\n		<li>Career Development / Talent Management (Basic)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Experience\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Min 1 year experience in IT Project or Business Project Improvement</li>\r\n		<li>Rookie / new entries without specific requirements but fulfilling most of the &ldquo;Specific character&rdquo; required will be considered, with 1-2 years intense personal development as senior staff. Supervise position will be given subject to result of development and performance.</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Skill Set\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>English &ndash; Intermediate</li>\r\n		<li>Computer Literacy - Intermediate</li>\r\n		<li>Communication skill &amp; Time Management</li>\r\n		<li>Planning and execution</li>\r\n		<li>Leadership &amp; coaching skill</li>\r\n		<li>Presentation Skill</li>\r\n		<li>Great team work</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specific Character</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High integrity</li>\r\n	<li>Independent</li>\r\n	<li>Discipline &amp; Punctual</li>\r\n	<li>Eager to learn &amp; Fast learner</li>\r\n	<li>Quality &amp; Result oriented</li>\r\n	<li>Self-motivated</li>\r\n	<li>Assertive</li>\r\n	<li>Resourceful</li>\r\n	<li>Good listener</li>\r\n	<li>Well organized</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Please send your detail resume or CV&nbsp;with photograph to : <u>Andri.Murfih@allianz.co.id</u>&nbsp;and <u>Elisabeth.Sutiono@allianz.co.id</u></strong></p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-21', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-31 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Agency Strategic Development Officer / Supervisor', 0),
