(56, 1, 'Fly Your Career with Sriwijaya Airlines', 'PT SRIWIJAYA AIR', '<p>We are PT SRIWIJAYA AIR, one of the biggest airline companyin Indonesiato exist as a regional airline which focuses on the quality of service with reliable human resources to support the company&rsquo;s development and welfare of employees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>JOB VACANCIES :</strong><br />\r\n1. Software Developer / Programmer<br />\r\n2. QA and System Support<br />\r\n3. Server / DCO Engineer<br />\r\n4. Business Intelligence Developer<br />\r\n5. Technical Support<br />\r\n6. Head of IT Logistics and Supply Chain</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements :</strong><br />\r\n- Male and Female,Max 30 years old.<br />\r\n- Bachelor Degree (S1) in Information and Technologymajor.<br />\r\n- Having 1 year experience with cumulative minimun GPA 2.75on a 4 point scale.Fresh Graduates with GPA &gt; 3 are welcome to apply.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>Software Developer</strong></u></span><br />\r\nFamiliar with Dreamweaver,eclipse/NetBeans and Having knowledge of Java C/C++/PHP,Oracle Database/SQL Server/Postgresql/Mysql,HTML(AJAX,JSON,XML) and Javascript/jQuery/Bootstrap.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>QA and System Support</strong></u></span><br />\r\nUnderstanding of system development life cycle and able to create test scenario,test cases and test script from the given functional design document</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>Server / DCO Engineer</strong></u></span><br />\r\nBasic OS knowledge (Windows,linux,Unix,Android, Vmware, etc),VCA/RHCSA or equivalent,VCP/RHCE will be an advantages,Full Driving License Essential and understanding Blade System Server and SAN/NAS storage are preferable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>NOC Engineer</strong></u></span><br />\r\nExperience with Juniper,HP and various hardware platforms including Cisco are preferable, understanding basic Networking (OSI Model),CCNA or equivalent,CCNP will be an advantages,Full Driving License Essential and advanced knowledge af common telecommunications technologies and protocols such as TCP/IP,Ethernet DNS,etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>Business intelligence Developer</strong></u></span><br />\r\nProficient knowledge in PL/SQL,SQL language, having knowledge of HTML 5,CSS3,javascript is a plus Experience with BI Tools like OBIEE,Qlikview is a significant plus,Highly energetic and self-motivated with strong data analysis skills,having knowledge in popular RDBMS such as database oracle mysql and postgresql.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>IT Technical Support</strong></u></span><br />\r\nUnderstand Networking concept,Basis OS Knowledge (Windows,Linux,Unix,Android,VMware,etc)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>Head of IT Logistics and Suplly Chain</strong></u></span><br />\r\nHaving Experience in logistic and supply chain area min 1 year Basic OS Knowledge (Windows,Linux,Unix,Android,VMware,etc)<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n- Actively in Organization experiences to be prior.<br />\r\n- Excellent health,no color blind (both partial or total).<br />\r\n- Excellentverbal and written communication in English.<br />\r\n- Good analytical and problem solving skills.<br />\r\n- Able to work in team and independently.<br />\r\n- Able to work under pressure.<br />\r\n- Willing to work extra hours as needed.<br />\r\n- High achiever and fast learner.<br />\r\n- Able to work in shift hour including weekend and public holiday for positions : System Support ,DCO Engineer NOC Engineer and IT Technical Support</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are interested and competent in accordance to the requirements of your education background base on each job vacancies positions above,apply your application letter and resume to recruitment@sriwijaya.co.id and put position name on the subject mail.</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2016-04-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-29 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Software Developer, Business Intelegence Development, Head of IT Logistic and Supply Chain, etc.', 0),
(57, 1, 'Are You a Good Teamplayer? Join Us!', 'PT. BANK BUMI ARTA Tbk.', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>PT. BANK BUMI ARTA Tbk.</strong></span><br />\r\n<em>Teman Anda Dalam Usaha</em><br />\r\n(BANK DEVISA) didirikan sejak tahun 1967</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Andakah yang Kami cari ?<br />\r\nJika anda seorang yang berkepribadian baik, menarik, suka tantangan, proaktif, komunikatif Teamplayer, dan memiliki persyaratan.<br />\r\nKami mengundang Anda untuk menempati posisi berikut :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Sales / Marketing ( AO )<br />\r\n2. Appraisal Staff ( Ap )<br />\r\n3. Audit Staff ( AU )<br />\r\n4. Officer Development Program ( ODP )<br />\r\n5. Review Kredit Staff ( RK )<br />\r\n6. Admin Kredit / Loan Center Staff ( LC )<br />\r\n7. Unit Manajemen Risiko Staff ( MR )<br />\r\n8. IT Development Staff ( ITD )<br />\r\n9. IT Support Staff ( ITS )</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Persyaratan Umum:</span></strong><br />\r\n- Pria / Wanita,max 27 Tahun<br />\r\n- Pendidikan min.D3.dengan IPK min 2.75<br />\r\n- Fresh Graduate,pengalaman di perbankan lebih disukai<br />\r\n- Penampilan menarik,ramah,<br />\r\n- Teliti,jujur,dan tanggung jawab dalam pekerjaan<br />\r\n- Mampu berkomunikasi dengan baik<br />\r\n- Mampu mengoperasikan computer<br />\r\n- Mampu bekerja di bawah tekanan dan ulet<br />\r\n- Untuk IT Development (ITD) menguasai coding Java<br />\r\n- Untuk posisi Review Kredit Staff (RK) &amp; Admin Kredit/Loan Center Staff (LC) menguasai jurnal dan akuntasi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kirimkan:<br />\r\nSurat Lamaran,CV , Fotocopy KTP,dan Foto Terbaru.Tuliskan kode jabatan dikiri atas amplop atau pada subject Email.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HR Recruitment: Jl.KH.Wahid Hasyim No 234 Jakarta Pusat 10250<br />\r\n(021) 2300893,2300455<br />\r\nEmail: hrd@bankbba.co.id</strong></p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2016-04-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-29 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Marketing, Audit Staff, Unit Manajemen Ris