(64, 1, 'Be Professional with Dynapack Asia', 'DYNAPACK INDONESIA', '<p>Head Office:<br />\r\n9th Floor, Dynaplast Tower, Jl. MH Thamrin, Lippo Karawaci<br />\r\nTangerang 15811, Banten - Indonesia<br />\r\nPhone :&nbsp;546 &nbsp;3111/546 1112-5; Fax.: (62 21) 5461266<br />\r\nwww.dynapackasia.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The leading and largest rigid plastic packaging company in Indonesia is looking for highly qualified professionals. We have 10 companies within the DYNAPACK ASIA group, across 5 countries (Indonesia, Thailand, Vietnam, Malaysia, and China), with a total of 27 manufacturing plants. We need people who are self-motivated and team players, good in following skills of which are English both oral and written, communication and interpersonal, and computer skills, to join us in a competitive environment for the following position:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Business Analyst (Code : BA)<br />\r\nQualifications:<br />\r\n1. Bachelor Degree (S1) with min. GPA 3.50 (Finance/Economic Management/Accounting/ Business Finance)&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. For Fresh Graduate<br />\r\n3. Fluent in English<br />\r\n4. Computer literate<br />\r\n5. Must be a self starter, independent, and good analytical skill<br />\r\n6. Good interpersonal skill and attitude<br />\r\n7. Willing to be located in Lippo Karawaci, Tangerang</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please submit your application letter, comprehensive resume, with a recent photograph (size of 3x4) and quote the position code on the top left envelope to:<br />\r\nCorporate HR<br />\r\nPT Dynapack Indonesia<br />\r\nDynaplast Tower 9-10th Floor<br />\r\nJl. MH Thamrin No. 1<br />\r\nLippo Karawaci, Tangerang 15811<br />\r\nOr<br />\r\neveline.hartono@dynapackasia.com not later than May 30, 2016.</p>\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2016-05-17', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-05-31 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Business Analyst', 0),
