(67, 1, 'Semen Bosova Buka Loker Trainee Program', 'PT SEMEN BOSOWA INDONESIA', '<p>PT. Semen Bosowa merupakan perusahaan perdagangan yang didirikan oleh H.M. Aksa Mahmud pada tanggal 22 Februari 1973. Pada awal berdirinya perusahaan ini bernama CV Moneter yang terletak di Makassar, Sulawesi Selatan. Dengan visi Menjadi pemain utama ekonomi nasional yang didukung oleh tenaga kerja yang prima, produk berkualitas, pelayanan terbaik, dan sistem yang terintegrasi, perusahaan ini melakukan perluasan industri yang dibagi dalam beberapa unit bisnis, yakni otomotif, semen, logistik &amp; transportasi, pertambangan, properti, jasa keuangan, infrastruktur, energi,media, dan multi bisnis.<br />\r\nSalah satu unit bisnis Bosowa adalah PT Semen Bosowa Maros. Unit ini merupakan salah satu unit usaha andalan yang dimiliki oleh Bosowa Grup. Produksi unit ini meliputi proses penggunaan bahan baku, proses produksi semen hingga proses pengiriman kepada konsumen. Setiap tahapan proses dilakukan secara profesional dengan bantuan para tenaga ahli di bidangnya.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Detil Pekerjaan<br />\r\nPosisi Yang Dinutuhkan:<br />\r\n1. Technical Trainee Program<br />\r\n2. Administrasi<br />\r\n3. Assistant Management<br />\r\n4. Analisis Kimia<br />\r\n5. Pengolahan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Persyaratan:<br />\r\n- Pria / Wanita<br />\r\n- Usia maksimal 30 tahun<br />\r\n- Pria, pengalaman minimal 1 tahun<br />\r\n- Pendidikan minimal D3, S1, sedrajat semua jurusan<br />\r\n- Memiliki Indeks Prestasi Kumulatif paling rendah 2,75<br />\r\n- Mampu mengoperasikan komputer(minimal Ms. Word &amp; Excel)<br />\r\n- Mampu berbahasa asing akan menjadi kelebihan<br />\r\n- Bersedia mengikuti interview di wilayah kerja PT. Semen Bosowa<br />\r\n- Bersedia ditempatkan di wilayah kerja PT. Semen Bosowa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Benefit:<br />\r\n&bull; Uang Makan &amp; Transport Rp. 27.000,-/hari<br />\r\n&bull; Tunjangan Asuransi / Jamsostek<br />\r\n&bull; Seragam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kelengakapan berkas lamaran:<br />\r\n&bull; Surat lamaran dan Daftar Riwayat Hidup<br />\r\n&bull; Fotocopy ijazah dan transkrip<br />\r\n&bull; Fotocopy KTP dan Pas Foto ukuran 4 x 6 cm<br />\r\n&bull; No. Hp / telepon dan Alamat email yang valid</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Silahkan kirim berkas lamaran anda ke email: (info@careersbosowa.com &nbsp;/ karir.bsw@gmail.com)<br />\r\nAtau kunjungi web kami di: careersbosowa.com</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2016-05-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-08 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Technical Trainee Program, Administrasi,  Assistant Management, Analisis Kimia, Pengolahan', 0),
(68, 1, 'Garena Looking for Designer and Web Developer', 'GARENA INDONESIA', '<p>WEB DEVELOPER<br />\r\n(Code : WebDev)<br />\r\nJob descriptions:<br />\r\n&bull; Write client &amp; server-side PHP/Python code that powers the user interface<br />\r\n&bull; Build new features and fix bugs<br />\r\n&bull; Write high-quality, clean, maintainable code using engineering best practices (unit testing, source control, continuous integration, automation, design patterns, etc.)<br />\r\n&bull; Collaborate with other software engineers, product managers, user experience designer, and operations engineers to build new web products</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Requirements:<br />\r\n&bull; Bachelor degree or higher in Computer Science or related field<br />\r\n&bull; In-depth understanding of data structures and algorithms<br />\r\n&bull; Familiar with at least one server side scripting language such as PHP<br />\r\n&bull; Intermediate-level knowledge of Object Oriented programming<br />\r\n&bull; Experience with fronted technologies (HTML, CSS, Javascript)<br />\r\n&bull; Proficient in Linux operating system, Apache/Nginx</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GRAPHIC DESIGNER<br />\r\n(Code: GrapDes)<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n&bull; Minimum S1 from Graphic Design or Visual Communication Design or other related major<br />\r\n&bull; Proficient in Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, etc.<br />\r\n&bull; Experienced in Graphic Illustration is a plus<br />\r\n&bull; Creative with knowledge of industry trends and think out of the box<br />\r\n&bull; Know about video editing is a plus<br />\r\n&bull; Fresh graduate / 1 year and above of relevant experience are welcome<br />\r\n&bull; Good attitude, must be open to new ideas<br />\r\n&bull; Good conceptualizing and organization skills<br />\r\n&bull; Able to work independently and enjoy working with a creative team</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PLEASE SEND YOUR RESUME TO HR-ID@GARENA.CO.ID<br />\r\nWITH FOLLOWING SUBJECT: POSITION_NAME</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-05-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-08 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Web Developer, Graphic Designer', 0),
(69, 1, 'PT Emerio Open for IT', 'PT EMERIO INDONESIA', '<p><strong>Graduate IT Consultant Trainee</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Fresh Graduate from reputable university with a degree of Information Technology / Computer Science / Technical background with minimum GPA of 3.00<br />\r\n&bull; Has good analytical thinking<br />\r\n&bull; Has Conceptual Knowledge in Relational Database Management System (RDBMS)<br />\r\n&bull; Has good knowledge of programming language skills, such as (Java, PHP / VB / C / C++ / .NET/ Mobile Apps)<br />\r\n&bull; Has drive, ambition, determination, eager to learn and good interpersonal skill<br />\r\n&bull; Good English communication skill both in written and verbal is essential</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Java Developer<br />\r\nRequirement:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor&#39;s Degree, Computer Science/Information Technology, Engineering (Computer/Telecommunication) or equivalent<br />\r\n&bull; Has minimum experience of 3 years incharge &nbsp;Java (J2EE) projects and JBoss<br />\r\n&bull; Good understanding and practice in Java / Java Enterprise Edition (knowledge in Java Connector Architecture and Java Management extension is definitely an advantage)<br />\r\n&bull; Good in application: Spring, Struts, Hibernate, Ibatis, etc<br />\r\n&bull; Experience in core banking application will be an advantage value</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>.NET Developer<br />\r\nRequirement :</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Bachelor degree majoring in Information Technology. A lower degree in combination of qualifying experience may be accepted in lieu of the bachelor degree<br />\r\n&bull; Candidate should have minimum 2 years experience in development of information system using .NET framework C# programming language for both web based and desktop environment<br />\r\n&bull; Strong hands on experience in Microsoft .NET programming (C#, VB .NET, ASP .NET)<br />\r\n&bull; Good knowledge and experience in &nbsp;Microsoft SQL Server 2000/2005 or Oracle Database would be an advantage<br />\r\n&bull; Reporting Tools (Crystal Report, Active Report, etc)<br />\r\n&bull; Experience with full software development life cycle (SDLC), software development, testing methodologies<br />\r\nSystem Analyst<br />\r\nRequirement:<br />\r\n&bull; Having 5+ years experience as System Analyst/Business Analyst<br />\r\n&bull; Must have strong &nbsp;Financial Data Analysis and reconciliation system<br />\r\n&bull; Having good in analyst and technical for transactional system, such as:<br />\r\n&nbsp; - Knowing about ATM Transaction (Withdraw/Deposit/Replenishment)<br />\r\n&nbsp; - Knowing about Credit Card Transaction(Visa/Master/Amex,etc)<br />\r\n&nbsp; - Knowing about BI RTGS Transaction, BI SKN Transaction, ArtaJasa Transaction<br />\r\n&nbsp; - Knowing about Telecom Payment, Electric Payment,etc<br />\r\n&nbsp; - Knowing about SWIFT Transaction(Nostro/Confirmation)<br />\r\n&nbsp; - Knowing about Other Payment System<br />\r\n&bull; Have good knowledge and experience in .Net, SQL server and Crystal reports</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ETL Consultant</strong><br />\r\nRequirement:<br />\r\n&bull; Graduate Degree in Information Technology from reputable university<br />\r\n&bull; Has minimum 2 years of experience in Data Warehouse / Business Intelligent / Data Integrator ETL software<br />\r\n&bull; Understanding and experience with ETL methodologies, Business Intelligence and data warehousing principles, approaches, technologies<br />\r\n&bull; Must have used ETL tools for data extraction &amp; aggregation works<br />\r\n&bull; Excellent hands on experience in software application development mainly focus on Microsoft Technologies like Microsoft .NET Framework, C#, Visual Basic.NET, ASP.NET, SQL Server,<br />\r\n&bull; Having Knowledge about &nbsp;:<br />\r\n&nbsp; - Database : Sybase, Oracle, Sql Server<br />\r\n&nbsp; - ETL Tools : Informatica, SSIS, Pentaho<br />\r\n&nbsp; - Operating System : Window, Linux</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.<strong>NET Web Developer</strong><br />\r\nRequirement :<br />\r\n&bull; Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor&#39;s Degree, Engineering (Computer/Telecommunication) or equivalent<br />\r\n&bull; Web Development<br />\r\n&bull; .Net Programming<br />\r\n&bull; MSSQL 2012<br />\r\n&bull; At least 2 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Oracle Finance Trainee</strong><br />\r\nRequirement:<br />\r\n&bull; Fresh Graduate from reputable university with Bachelor degree in Computer Accounting, Finance Management, Accounting from reputable university with minimum GPA 3.00&nbsp;<br />\r\n&bull; Max 25 years old<br />\r\n&bull; Good understanding of basic accounting and financial management&nbsp;<br />\r\n&bull; Ability to focus on detail and accuracy&nbsp;<br />\r\n&bull; Computer literate and adept in MS Excel and relevant financial software tools<br />\r\n&bull; Good interpersonal skills and a team work player<br />\r\n&bull; Good command of English both in written and verbal</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Marketing Communication Officer<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n&bull; Female, Minimum 1 years marketing experience, fresh graduate welcome to apply<br />\r\n&bull; Experience of mange social media (Content, design visual, etc)<br />\r\n&bull; Excellent communication skills<br />\r\n&bull; A good working knowledge of InDesign and Photoshop.<br />\r\n&bull; Understanding of Word press and other web tools and applications, blogs and online communities and social networks<br />\r\n&bull; Strong copywriting skills<br />\r\n&bull; The ability to plan, priorities and manage workload delivering projects to a good standard &amp; meeting deadlines<br />\r\n&bull; Excellent IT skills including programmers related to communicating online (email &amp; social media channels). Experience of Mailchimp would be advantageous.<br />\r\n&bull; The ability to work on own initiative and as part of a team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you consider yourself as a strong and convincing personality with total dedication to quality and customer satisfaction, you are welcome to be part of Emerio family. Please kindly send your comprehensive resume with the code subject to:<br />\r\nTalent.acquisition@emeriocorp.com<br />\r\nOr<br />\r\nRecruitment.admin@emeriocorp.com</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2016-05-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-10 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Oracle Finance Trainee,  Java Developer, Graduate IT Consultant Trainee, dll.', 0),
