(94, 1, 'Join PKG Group as Cinematographer', 'PKG', '<p>PKG is holding group consists of various exciting business units such as entertainment, beauty products, media production, agroprocessing industry, and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cinematographer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Responsibilities</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Creating the visual identity, or look, of the film. Dicsover the photographic heart of a screenplay</li>\r\n	<li>Working with the team to achieve the best possible result</li>\r\n	<li>Managing all visual aspects of filming: from ordering and overseeing equipment to recess to reviewing footage</li>\r\n	<li>Conduct research and preparation including carrying out technical recess of locations</li>\r\n	<li>Prepare a list of all required items, including shot list, floor plan, lights, camera, lenses and all accessories etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Able to operate the camera during the shoot</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Requirements</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Minimum 1 year industry experience as cinematographer or camera operator</li>\r\n	<li>Creative and passionate about filmmaking</li>\r\n	<li>Have good technical knowledge of digital camera processes and know all about camera equipment</li>\r\n	<li>Have in depth knowledge of lighting techniques and how to achieve them</li>\r\n	<li>Know about photography and moving images</li>\r\n	<li>Have artistic and good colour vision</li>\r\n	<li>Pay precise attention to detail</li>\r\n	<li>Able to take decisions quickly and flexible in order to adapt ideas instantly</li>\r\n	<li>Have excellent communication skills</li>\r\n	<li>Able to give and accept direction</li>\r\n	<li>Diplomatic and tactful when working together as a team</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Send your CV and portofolio to:<br />\r\n<a href=\"mailto:deriancinema@gmail.com\">deriancinema@gmail.com</a> and <a href=\"mailto:fitrahutama@gmail.com\">fitrahutama@gmail.com</a><br />\r\nOnly short listed candidates will be contacted.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Puncak Keemasan Group