(98, 1, 'Motion Graphic Designer at PKG', 'PKG', '<p>PKG is holding group consists of various exciting business units such as entertainment, beauty products, media production, agroprocessing industry, and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>MOTION GRAPHIC DESIGNER</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Design and animate custom motion graphic as standalone projects or integrated with the video</li>\r\n	<li>Develop unique creative concepts, designs, and storyboarding</li>\r\n	<li>Work closely with producers and editors on the Creative team as well as other learns within the Marketing Department</li>\r\n	<li>Lend a hand with production equipment for in-house video shoots</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Minimum 1 year motion design experience as part of either a creative, marketing, or post-production team</li>\r\n	<li>Proficient in After Effects, Photoshop and Illustrator</li>\r\n	<li>Comfortable doing basic editing in Premiere or willing to learn</li>\r\n	<li>Familiar with color theory and color correction</li>\r\n	<li>Strong sense for composition, layout and a respect for typography</li>\r\n	<li>Committed to ongoing education in motion design, current conceptual &amp; Stylistic trends</li>\r\n	<li>Well organized and capable of handling multiple ongoing assignments with many subtasks</li>\r\n	<li>Comfortable learning new software programs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Send your CV and Portofolio to:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:deriancinema@gmail.com\">deriancinema@gmail.com</a> and <a href=\"mailto:fitrahutama@gmail.com\">fitrahutama@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Only short listed candidates will be contacted</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Puncak Keemasan Group</strong><br />\r\nElectronic City Building 3<sup>rd</sup> floor<br />\r\nJl. Alam Sutera Boulevard, Serpong Utara<br />\r\nTangerang Selatan, Banten 15320<br />\r\nIndonesia</p>\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0,