(119, 1, 'Join in Talenta', 'Talenta (www.talenta.co)', '<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Talenta (www.talenta.co)</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Web Developer</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Description of duties:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Develop product and create new features<br />\r\n&bull; Fixing bugs and troubleshooting<br />\r\n&bull; Report work progress to leader daily</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Age maximum 27 years old<br />\r\n&bull; Education minimum D3 / S1 Degree in Information Technology or Information System from a reputable institution or equivalent<br />\r\n&bull; A self motivated and disciplined individual<br />\r\n&bull; Skills Advance Knowledge in PHP, HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, JQuery &amp; Ajax is must:&nbsp;<u>1-2 years of experience of Web Development using any Web Framework</u> and&nbsp;<u>Familiar with Yii Framework</u><br />\r\n&bull; Work well independently and in a team setting<br />\r\n&bull; Able to work under pressure and within a specific timeline<br />\r\n&bull; Open to new experiences and able to handle uncertainties<br />\r\n&bull; Familiar with other programming / scripting language such as Python / Ruby will be advantage<br />\r\n&bull; Fluent in English will be advantage</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. HR Staff</strong><br />\r\nWe are looking for Passionate &amp; Energic Candidate who will join us in HR Department Team.<br />\r\nThis position will handle recruitment function both administration &amp; operational activities. <strong>The responsibilities more likely:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Administer all documentation process related recruitment activities.<br />\r\n&bull; Prepare employee contracts as required, making contract &amp; discussing contract with employee.<br />\r\n&bull; Update &amp; Maintain employee data, employee attendance, absence, annual leave, etc.<br />\r\n&bull; Manage BPJS Kesehatan &amp; Ketenagakerjaan employee<br />\r\n&bull; Sourcing all candidate related qualification needed<br />\r\n&bull; Maintain all database related all recruit process<br />\r\n&bull; Coordinate with user in accordance to fullfillment<br />\r\n&bull; Report all recruitment process (weekly &amp; monthly)<br />\r\n&bull; Assist the recruitment section head for recruit progress<br />\r\n<strong>Requirement:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Candidate must possess at least Bachelor Degree of Pychology or related field<br />\r\n&bull; Fresh Graduate are welcome apply<br />\r\n&bull; Required skill: Admin activity, Recruiting<br />\r\n&bull; At least 1 year working experience in the related field is required for this position<br />\r\n&bull; Full-Time position (s) available</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Application Support<br />\r\nDescription of duties:<br />\r\n&bull; Support and give problem solving to clients<br />\r\n&bull; Report to manager about client needs and problem regularly<br />\r\n&bull; Follow up exist clients for payroll process every month</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Requirements:<br />\r\n&bull; Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor Degree, any field<br />\r\n&bull; Fresh graduate are welcomed<br />\r\n&bull; Knowing about payroll like tax, BPJS, overtime, and the others is added value<br />\r\n&bull; Fast Learner and independent<br />\r\n&bull; Comfortable with numbers</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Application Specialist</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Description of duties:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Assist client to setup application appropriate with clients requirements<br />\r\n&bull; Provide consultancy for client about best practice HRIS &amp; Payroll in Indonesia<br />\r\n&bull; Support and give problem solving to clients<br />\r\n&bull; Gather client requirement and implement the system<br />\r\n&bull; Test the application or bug fixing and new features that created by developer team<br />\r\n&bull; Report to manager about client needs and problem regularly</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor&#39;s Degree, any field<br />\r\n&bull; At least 1 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position, Fresh Graduate are welcomed<br />\r\n&bull; Knowing about payroll like tax, BPJS, overtime and the others is preferable<br />\r\n&bull; Fast learner and independent<br />\r\n&bull; Comfortable with numbers and meeting clients<br />\r\n<strong>Benefit:</strong><br />\r\nBPJS Ketenagakerjaan &amp; BPJS Kesehatan<br />\r\nSend&nbsp;your CV to:lita@talenta.co</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, '2016-08-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-09-15 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Web Developer, HR Staff, etc.', 0),
(120, 1, 'Urgently Needed for Game Level One', 'Game Level One', '<p><strong>GAME LEVEL ONE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lowongan Pekerjaan<br />\r\n<strong>Server/ Back-End Programmer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sebuah perusahaan yang bergerak di bidang Game Development di Jembatan Dua, Pluit, Jakarta Utara<br />\r\nmembutuhkan sumber daya manusia untuk posisi Server/ Back-end Programmer dengan:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tugas Umum:<br />\r\n- Maintain server yang sudah ada.<br />\r\n- Memastikan keaktifan server.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kemampuan Yang Dibutuhkan:<br />\r\n- Pendidikan minimal D3 (Fresh Graduated are welcome to apply).<br />\r\n- Pengalaman minimal 2 tahun.<br />\r\n- Memiliki pengalaman dengan HTML, Ajax (jQuery/Ext-Js/Mootools), CSS, PHP<br />\r\n- Pengalaman dengan Framework PHP Khususnya Codeigniter atau Laravel<br />\r\n- Memiliki pengalaman dalam CMS (Joomla, Wordpress)<br />\r\n- Mengerti konsep database<br />\r\n- Memiliki pengalaman membuat API</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sales/ Marketing</strong><br />\r\n- Mencari klien dan melakukan presentasi penawaran kepada klien<br />\r\n- Memberikan solusi kepada klien<br />\r\n- Menangani permasalahan/ hambatan yang ditemui di lapangan<br />\r\n- Bertanggung jawab atas permintaan yang masuk<br />\r\n- Mengadakan event dari mulai persiapan sampai dengan evaluasi<br />\r\nPersyaratan:<br />\r\n- Pendidikan min. D3<br />\r\n- Pengalaman 3 - 4 tahun.<br />\r\n- Fresh Graduate with relevant experience are welcome to apply.<br />\r\n- Lebih diutamakan pernah bekerja di Education Agency<br />\r\n- Lebih diutamakan memiliki pengalaman Digital Marketing/ Social Media.<br />\r\n- Bersedia melakukan perjalanan dinas, dalam maupun luar negeri.<br />\r\n- Menguasai Bahasa Inggris Aktif.<br />\r\n- Memiliki passion di bidang games dan pendidikan.<br />\r\n- Memiliki kemampuan problem solving yang baik.<br />\r\n- Mampu bekerja sendiri dan bekerja sama dengan tim.<br />\r\n- Memiliki kemampuan komunikasi yang baik.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Game Programmer</strong><br />\r\nTugas Umum:<br />\r\n- Mengembangkan mockup, test, dan real project game sesuai dengen standar dan timeline yang telah ditentukan<br />\r\n- Memberikan masukan dari sisi technical/ programming tentang project yang sedang dikerjakan.<br />\r\n- Melakukan maintenance dan pengembangan game yang sudah ada.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Persyaratan:<br />\r\n- Pendidikan min. D3 (Fresh Graduated are welcome to apply).<br />\r\n- Lebih diutamakan memiliki pengalaman/ portfolio membuat games.<br />\r\n- Mahir menggunakan Unity Game Engine.<br />\r\n- Pengalaman menggunakan Corona SDK, Unity 3D, Cocos 2D, Buildbox dan Construct 2 serta bisa tools game lainnya.<br />\r\n- Pengalaman meng-upload game ke Google Playstore dan atau Apple App Store.<br />\r\n- Memiliki pengetahuan proses pembuatan video games.<br />\r\n- Memiliki passion/ hobi bermain game (gamer).<br />\r\n- Memiliki kemampuan problem solving yang baik.<br />\r\n- Mampu bekerja sendiri dan bekerja sama dengan tim.<br />\r\n- Memiliki kemampuan komunikasi yang baik.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jika Anda berminat, segera kirimkan CV dan portfolio/ link portfolio ke:<br />\r\n<strong>hr@gamelevelone.com<br />\r\nApakah anda memiliki portfolio games?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2D Artist</strong><br />\r\nTugas Umum:<br />\r\nMembuat mockup, test, dan real assets (concept, background, UI, character) sesuai dengen standar dan timeline yang telah ditentukan.<br />\r\nMemberikan masukan dari sisi art tentang project yang sedang dikerjakan dan game design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Persyaratan:<br />\r\n- Pendidikan min. D3 (Fresh Graduated are welcome to apply).<br />\r\n- Lebih diutamakan memiliki pengalaman/ portfolio membuat games.<br />\r\n- Memiliki pengetahuan tentang Ilustrasi, User Interface, User Experience, dan Animasi 2D, akan menjadi nilai lebih.<br />\r\n- Menguasai software pengolahan gambar Raster (Photoshop, Sai) dan Vector (Illustrator, CorelDraw).<br />\r\n- Memiliki passion/ hobi bermain game (gamer).<br />\r\n- Memiliki kemampuan problem solving yang baik.<br />\r\n- Mampu bekerja sendiri dan bekerja sama dengan tim.<br />\r\n- Memiliki kemampuan komunikasi yang baik.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jika Anda berminat, segera kirimkan CV dan portfolio/ link portfolio ke:<br />\r\n<strong>hr@gamelevelone.com</strong></p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-08-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-08-31 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Server/ Back-End Programmer, Sales/ Marketing, Game Programmer, 2D Artist', 0),
(121, 1, 'Moonlay Open for Recruitment', 'PT Moonlay Technologies', '<p>Beberapa posisi yang sedang dibuka adalah:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>1.Junior Developer (macro based)</strong></span><br />\r\nResponsibilities<br />\r\n&bull; Actively and participate in application development&nbsp;according to business requirements and needs.<br />\r\nThe incumbent will require communication skill and analytical skill to gather business needs/requirements. Incumbent will also needs to develop the application using macro programming.<br />\r\n&bull; Actively give ideas regarding project to create and produce a good application.<br />\r\n&bull; Learn how to implement programming best practices to increase your performance and deliverables.<br />\r\n&bull; Must be willing to work at Sudirman and South of Jakarta.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Academic Qualification<br />\r\n&bull; Undergraduate degree (S1/B.Sc./B.A.) with GPA 3.0 from reputable universities<br />\r\n&bull; Majoring in Computer Science, System Information, Informatics Engineering or other relevant majors<br />\r\n&bull; Experience as Teaching Assistant, Lab. Assistant or Relevant Academic Organization is an advantage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Attitude Qualification<br />\r\n&bull; Attractive personality<br />\r\n&bull; Discipline, Hardworking, able to work under pressure<br />\r\n&bull; Result Oriented with good process justification<br />\r\n&bull; Excellent English<br />\r\n&bull; Communicative &amp; social awareness<br />\r\n&bull; Good individual and team player<br />\r\n&bull; Know to have fun</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aptitude Qualification<br />\r\n&bull; Excellent OOA/D and OOP understanding<br />\r\n&bull; Minimum 1 year experience in the same position. Fresh graduates are welcome to apply<br />\r\n&bull; Understanding in macro programming language and Ms. Excel C# or .NET proficiency (or other relevant .NET programming language) will be advantage<br />\r\n&bull; Understanding on Microsoft SQLServer Technologies<br />\r\n&bull; Knowledge on development architecture, design patterns and practices in an advantage<br />\r\n&bull; Knowledge on user interface programming, behavior and design is an advantage</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>2. Junior Developer (desktop/web/mobile application)</strong></span><br />\r\nResponsibilities<br />\r\n&bull; Actively and participate in application development&nbsp;according to business requirements and needs.<br />\r\n&bull; The incumbent will require communication skill and analytical skill to gather business needs along with the scrum master.<br />\r\n&bull; Actively give ideas regarding project to create and produce a good application.<br />\r\n&bull; Learn how to implement programming best practices to increase your performance and deliverables.<br />\r\n&bull; Develop desktop/web/mobile application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Academic Qualification<br />\r\n&bull; Undergraduate degree (S1/B.Sc./B.A.) with GPA 3.0 from reputable universities<br />\r\n&bull; Majoring in Computer Science, System Information, Informatics Engineering or other relevant majors<br />\r\n&bull; Experience as Teaching Assistant, Lab. Assistant or Relevant Academic Organization is an advantage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Attitude Qualification<br />\r\n&bull; Attractive personality<br />\r\n&bull; Discipline, Hardworking, able to work under pressure<br />\r\n&bull; Result Oriented with good process justification<br />\r\n&bull; Excellent English<br />\r\n&bull; Communicative &amp; social awareness<br />\r\n&bull; Good individual and team player<br />\r\n&bull; Know to have fun</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aptitude Qualification<br />\r\n&bull; Excellent OOA/D and OOP understanding<br />\r\n&bull; Minimum 1 year experience in the same position, fresh graduates are welcome to apply<br />\r\n&bull; Understanding C# or .NET or mobile programming language proficiency (or other relevant .NET programming language)<br />\r\n&bull; Understanding on desktop, client server, network and web programming or mobile application<br />\r\n&bull; Understanding on Microsoft SQLServer Technologies<br />\r\n&bull; Understanding on Windows Presentation Foundation<br />\r\n&bull; Understanding the concept of Model-View-ViewModel design pattern<br />\r\n&bull; Knowledge on Oracle and MySQL DBMS in an advantage<br />\r\n&bull; Knowledge on development architecture, design patterns and practices in an advantage<br />\r\n&bull; Knowledge on user interface programming, behavior and design is an advantage<br />\r\n&bull; Knowledge on other programming language is an advantage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bagi yang berminat silahkan kirimkan ke email: ratna.ayu@moonlay.com</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2016-08-22', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-09-16 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Junior Developer', 0),
(122, 1, 'Lowongan D3/S1 di Hama Pest Control', 'PT Karunia Perkasa Jaya (Hama Pest Control)', '<p><strong>Hama Pest Control </strong>adalah perusahaan jasa yang bergerak di bidang Pengendalian Hama. Saat ini kami mengajak anda untuk menjadi kandidat di perusahaan kami,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hama Pest Control membuka lowongan pekerjaan sebagai:<br />\r\n&bull; Sales/Marketing (6 orang)<br />\r\n&bull; Admin (1 orang)<br />\r\n&bull; Akunting/Pembukuan (1 orang)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Syarat Pelamar:<br />\r\n- Lulusan Min. D3/S1<br />\r\n- Pria / Wanita usia maks.28 th<br />\r\n- Status Single<br />\r\n- Mau bekerja keras &amp; maju<br />\r\n- Suka tantangan<br />\r\n- Berpenampilan menarik<br />\r\n- Memiliki kendaraan pribadi (khusus sales)<br />\r\n- Memiliki SIM A/C (khusus sales)<br />\r\n- Bersedia ditempatkan dimana saja</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kirim Lamaran Via Pos ke alamat : <strong>Jl. Raya Meruya Selatan No. 27A, Kembangan Meruya Utara &ndash; JakBar 11620, Tlp. 58906178.</strong><br />\r\nEmail: <strong>catherine@vibrand.biz</strong><br />\r\nNote: Lamaran diterima paling lambat tanggal <strong><u>25 Agustus 2016</u></strong> - Bila terpilih, Interview panggilan via telpon dan Interview dilakukan akhir bulan Agustus 2016 di Kantor Alam Sutra, Serpong.</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2016-08-22', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-09-16 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Marketing, Admin, Accounting', 0),
(123, 1, 'Kesempatan Bersama Bless Cosmetics', 'PT Utama Bakti Farmasi', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Digital Marketing Executive</strong></span><br />\r\n<strong>KUALIFIKASI</strong><br />\r\n- Berkepribadian baik dan ber‐integritas,<br />\r\n- Usia maksimal 28 tahun, diutamakan wanita<br />\r\n- Menguasai bahasa Inggis<br />\r\n- S1 dibidang Multimedia atau IT<br />\r\n- Pengalaman minimal 1 tahun dibagian IT atau Digital Marketing<br />\r\n- Menguasai hal‐hal teknis berkaitan dengan pengembangan website dan transaksi online<br />\r\n- Mengikuti dan memahami perkembangan dunia social media dan digital marketing</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GAMBARAN PEKERJAAN</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Mendukung semua kegiatan divisi promosi yang berkaitan dengan digital marketing<br />\r\n- Mengelola hal‐hal teknis berkaitan dengan kegiatan digital marketing:<br />\r\nWebsite Maintenance<br />\r\nOnline Shopping<br />\r\nDigital advertising, dll.<br />\r\n- Merencanakan program &ndash;program dan mengelola hal‐hal teknis berkaitan dengan social media (FB, Twitter, Instagram, dll)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kirim Lamaran:&nbsp;hrd@bless.co.id<br />\r\n<strong>atau</strong><br />\r\nKH.Mas Mansyur No.76<br />\r\nTelp. 021&ndash;315 1463<br />\r\nJakarta Pusat 10230</p>\r\n', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2016-08-22', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-09-17 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Digital Marketing Executive', 0);
