(124, 1, 'Netpolitan Needs Creative People', 'PT. Netpolitan', '<p>Netpolitan is a creative content development company that makes the eLearning as its main product. Currently has been working with a number of client companies large and prominent from various fields. As a growing company, we are inviting qualified individuals to join our team for the following available positions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Character Designer</strong></span><br />\r\nWe are looking for greathearted, committed, and hardworking Illustrator to Join Our Team in a fun and youthful work environment.<br />\r\nJob Responsibilities:<br />\r\n- Responsible for the design in e-learning project.<br />\r\n- Operates effectively as a member of the product development team<br />\r\n- Collaborate with team on e-learning design initiatives and strategies</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a Graphic Designer, you must be:<br />\r\n- Creative and have great sense of art.<br />\r\n- Good skills in design software.<br />\r\n- Have good interpersonal and communication skills.<br />\r\n- Be able to work with tight deadlines.<br />\r\n- Proactive, productive, and efficient.<br />\r\n- Strong individual as well as good team player.<br />\r\n- Ability to adjust and adapt in an ever-changing environment.<br />\r\nTechnical Requirements:<br />\r\n- Male/Female max 35 years old<br />\r\n- Fresh graduate welcome to apply<br />\r\n- Able to show a great portfolio</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Flash Animator</span></strong><br />\r\nWe are looking for greathearted, committed, and hardworking Animator to Join Our Team in a fun and youthful work environment.<br />\r\nIf the following describes you, we&rsquo;d love to hear from you:<br />\r\n- A loveable personality with a good heart and good attitude<br />\r\n- Highly self-motivated and hardworking<br />\r\n- Able to work fast, independently and under pressure<br />\r\n- Organized and have a good eye for details<br />\r\n- A team player, able to work and communicate well with others<br />\r\n- Non- idealistic, open minded and willing to learn<br />\r\nAs an Animator, you must be:<br />\r\n- Interested in animation and characters design<br />\r\n- Mastering min basic action script<br />\r\n- Mastering 2D and 3D animation<br />\r\n- Can use Adobe Flash<br />\r\n- Must be able work in a fast-paced in a high-pressure environment Technical<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n- Male/Female max 35 years old<br />\r\n- Fresh graduate welcome to apply<br />\r\n- Able to show a great portfolio</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Flash Programmer</strong></span><br />\r\nWe are looking for greathearted, committed, and hardworking Programmer to Join Our Team in a fun and youthful work environment.<br />\r\nIf the following describes you, we&rsquo;d love to hear from you:<br />\r\n- A loveable personality with a good heart and good attitude<br />\r\n- Highly self-motivated and hardworking<br />\r\n- Able to work fast, independently and under pressure<br />\r\n- Organized and have a good eye for details<br />\r\n- A team player, able to work and communicate well with others<br />\r\n- Non- idealistic, open minded and willing to learn<br />\r\nJob Responsibilities:<br />\r\n- Create interactive educational contents for teaching and learning based on storyboard using Flash and Action Script<br />\r\n- To integrate all Flash assets (text, voice, animation, simulation) into a ready-use integration content Technical<br />\r\nRequirements:<br />\r\n- Male / Female; max 35 years old<br />\r\n- Experienced in using Flash and Action Script 2.0 is a must<br />\r\n- Experienced in Action Script 3.0, XML, PHP is a plus<br />\r\n- Familiar with Android SDK and IOS SDK would be an advantage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are a qualified candidate, please submit your application that must include the following:<br />\r\nFull CV + Recent Photograph<br />\r\nPortfolio (one.zip file of your combined portfolios is Preferable)<br />\r\nStated Expected Salary<br />\r\nTo: <strong>vonny@netpolitanteam.com</strong></p>\r\n', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-08-22', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-09-16 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Character Designer, Flash Animator, etc.', 0),
