(165, 1, 'Biogreen Open Recruitment', 'Biogreen Science', '<p><strong>Biogreen Science is a fast growing company focused on health and beauty industry. Our company has scored 5 featured products, and we are still on our way to develop more revolutionary products. We also have won 2 prestigious awards for our great company&rsquo;s service and innovative products.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Finance Staff</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Handle administration and petty cash</li>\r\n	<li>Compile Financial report</li>\r\n	<li>Prepare and able to calculate PPh 21, PPh 23,PPh 4 (2), PPh 25, and PPN</li>\r\n	<li>Doing monthly tax payment and reporting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bachelor degree in Finance / Accounting</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum 3 years experience in Accounting and Tax reporting</li>\r\n	<li>Fluent in English ( Compulsory)</li>\r\n	<li>Computer literate MS Office</li>\r\n	<li>Good Knowledge in Financial Report and Tax rules</li>\r\n	<li>Good communication and analytical skills</li>\r\n	<li>Can Work Under Pressure/deadline</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>​</strong><strong>2. Customer Filed Survey</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bachelor degree in High School</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum 1 Experience</li>\r\n	<li>Computer literate MS Office</li>\r\n	<li>Good communication and analytical skills</li>\r\n	<li>Can Work Under Pressure/deadline</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Bussiness Development</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Key job responsibilities will include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Recommend marketing strategies for the purpose of enhancing company sales</li>\r\n	<li>Assists with writing proposals, including project and proposal coordination and liaising with customers, and related parties</li>\r\n	<li>Manage day-to-day operational issues and admin related stuff</li>\r\n	<li>Perform other duties as required</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Excellent written and verbal communication skill both in English and Bahasa</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor&#39;s degree required from reputable university</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate about company&#39;s growth and able to work in a fast paced environment</li>\r\n	<li>Proactive, responsible, organized and able to work independently</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to adapt to challenges in a constantly evolving start-up environment</li>\r\n	<li>Good team player with multi countries exposure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Background from Customer Service and Account Management will be an additional advantage.​</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Copywriter</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt\"><strong>Responsibilities :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Preparing market-oriented articles for use in for broadcasting or publications.</li>\r\n	<li>To write other materials to promote different products.</li>\r\n	<li>Often to work with the brand manager to create advertising slogans and themes, and may be involved in the actual advertising of the product, including: Announcements, Articles, Quizzes, Resource boxes and introductions, Advertisements promoting the publication and Content for client advertisements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Age between 22 - 27 years old.</li>\r\n	<li>Min. D3 in Graphic Design/Visual Communication Design/Advertising.</li>\r\n	<li>Min. 2 years of relevant experience, &amp; capable in operating related programs.</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to write clearly and concisely, basic comprehension of layout and design, &amp; capability of varying writing tone and style.</li>\r\n	<li>Editing and proofreading skills.</li>\r\n	<li>Effective verbal communication skills.</li>\r\n	<li>Research gathering and analysis ability.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong grammar skills, word processing, and computer knowledge.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. Multimedia</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Male/female. Max 27 years old</li>\r\n	<li>Candidate must posses at least bachelor&rsquo;s degree in art/design/creative multimedia, mass communication or equivalent</li>\r\n	<li>At least 1 year of working experience in related field is required in this position.</li>\r\n	<li>Able to operate designing programs (adobe photoshop or adobe illustrator)</li>\r\n	<li>Able to operate video editing program is a must (adobe premiere and after effect)</li>\r\n	<li>Candidate must have a good sense of creativity</li>\r\n	<li>Able to work under pressure</li>\r\n	<li>Able to operate camera (take photos or video) is preferable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt\"><strong>Senior Marketing Head</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>S1/S2 degree with around 3-5 years experiences in marketing of consumer goods</li>\r\n	<li>English profiency &amp; mandarin literacy</li>\r\n	<li>Good analytical and interpersonal skill</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6. Assistant Creative director</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Female, max 27 years old</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor degree in English literature or art and design</li>\r\n	<li>Fluent in written and spoken English</li>\r\n	<li>Experienced in copywriting or editing</li>\r\n	<li>Have keen eyes and great understanding of English grammar and EYD bahasa Indonesia to proofread articles both in Bahasa and English</li>\r\n	<li>Candidate must have a good sense of creativity</li>\r\n	<li>Able to work under pressure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Send letter of application and your full CV to email <a href=\"mailto:hrd@biogreen.com\">hrd@biogreen.com</a> (put the position as email subject )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Or can come directly to PT. Bio Organik Nusantara. Jalan Cikini Raya. 58Q. Ruko Perkantoran Cikini. Jakarta Pusat.&nbsp;T: +62 218 370 8920 - T: +62 218 370 8922<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.biogreenscience.com\">www.biogreenscience.com</a></p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2016-09-09', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-07 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Many job vacancies', 0),
