(215, 1, 'Vivo Smartphone', 'Vivo Smartphone', '<p>ABOUT Vivo is a leading global smart phone brand focusing on introducing products with professional-grade audio, extraordinary appearance, and fast and smooth user experience. Vivo was founded in 2009 as a sub-brand of BBK Electronics. The brand entered the telecommunication and consumer electronics industry with landline phones and wireless phones. In 2011, Vivo started manufacturing and marketing its own range of smart phones. Vivo entered the Indian market in 2014. Currently 20,000 operators work in Vivo, and 3,000 engineers are in four R&amp;D centers in Dongguan, Shenzhen, Nanjing and Chongqing. From hardware design and manufacture, to software development (Android based Funtouch OS), Vivo has built a complete and sustainable ecosystem.</p>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2017-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-07 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, '5dd890136c4d3170ed8b24a6fe39dfb8f6760862.jpg', 'df9588c8cd9dede69a45491f59406ab07f1ba64d.png', 1, '', 0),
