(231, 1, 'Asia Pulp and Paper (Sinarmas Group)', 'Asia Pulp and Paper (Sinarmas Group)', '<p>APP is the world&rsquo;s largest vertically integrated pulp and paper company with total combined of over 10 million tons per annum. Over the years, we have significantly expanded our operations through simultaneous acquisition and expansion of pulp and paper mills around the world. Until today, APP has marketed its products to more than 120 countries across five continents.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To continously support sustainable business growth, we are looking for talented individuals to join our team as</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>FINANCE</strong> <strong>/ ACCOUNTING OFFICER (FA</strong><strong>O</strong><strong>)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>TREASURY OFFICER (TO)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>LOGISTIC OFFICER (LO)</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>General requirements:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hold min Bachelor degree, from reputable university with min GPA 3.00</li>\r\n	<li>Preferable graduates the following major\r\n	<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n		<li>No 1,2 &ndash; Accounting/ Finance/ Tax</li>\r\n		<li>No 3 &ndash; Operation</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Proficient in Microsoft Office program usage (Excel, Power Point)</li>\r\n	<li>Language skill(s): English both oral &amp; written, and Mandarin (would be an advantage)</li>\r\n	<li>Posses WINNING attitude, CARING personality and approach, DO everything with excellence</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2017-05-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-07-31 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Finance/Accounting Officer (FAO), Treasury Officer (TO), Logistic Officer (LO)', 0),
(229, 1152, 'Part Time Graphic Designer', 'Dimbleweb', '<div class=\"panel-body padding-horizontal-double padding-vertical-double\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Dimbleinc adalah suatu Agensi penyedia jasa desain dan pembuatan website (Website Design &amp; Development) yang berlokasi di Gading Serpong, Tangerang.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saat ini, kami sedang mencari seorang Desainer Grafis untuk menjadi salah satu anggota tim tetap Dimbleinc, dan turut serta bersama kami mewujudkan visi Dimbleinc menjadi salah satu Agensi Website terbaik di Indonesia</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Tanggung Jawab Pekerjaan :</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>1. Menyediakan berbagai jenis desain untuk kebutuhan internal (seperti banner, flyer, slideshow, dan gambar &ndash; gambar lain untuk kebutuhan promosi Agensi)<br />\r\n2. Menyediakan berbagai jenis desain untuk kebutuhan eksternal (berhubungan dengan klien, seperti desain website, logo, icon, dll)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Syarat Pengalaman :</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<div>Memiliki Portfolio Desain (flyer ,brosur, logo, desain web, dll)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Keahlian :</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>1. Adobe Photoshop (utama)<br />\r\n2. Adobe Illustrator (tambahan)<br />\r\n3. Adobe Flash (tambahan)<br />\r\n4. Adobe Dreamweaver / Sublime Text / Notepad++ (tambahan)<br />\r\n5. HTML5 &amp; CSS3 (tambahan)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Kualifikasi :</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>1. Memiliki Passion di bidang Desain Grafis<br />\r\n2. Mampu memenuhi tuntutan jam kerja minimal (18 jam per minggu)<br />\r\n3. Wajib menunjukkan Portfolio Desain yang pernah dibuat<br />\r\n4. Memiliki Portfolio Desain untuk Desain Website (diutamakan)<br />\r\n5. Memiliki kepribadian baik, mau belajar, serta Team Oriented<br />\r\n6. Berdomisili di Gading Serpong (diutamakan) atau daerah sekitar Tangerang</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2017-05-03', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, '8d64214fd9fcb5a4c8940a7e77a80f8b4c9dadb9.png', 1, 'Graphic Designer', 0),
(230, 1, 'PT Ultra Prima Abadi', 'PT Ultra Prima Abadi', '<p>For more than a half century, Orang Tua Group has been in the business of processing natural ingredients and turning them into quality foods products that have become the choice of consumers. Through research and innovation, Orang Tua Group has come up with unique products that lead the market. Orang Tua Group products have earned a special place in the hearts of its consumers. We believe that people play the main role in this company. A good environment and workplace support our people to grow and achieve their goals. We invite you, together with us, to achieve your goals and be our future leaders!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Positions: Marketing Staff, Accounting Staff, and Budget Control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Requirements&nbsp;:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">1. &nbsp;Fresh Graduate (1, 2)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">2. Experienced (3)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">3. Minimum GPA 3.00 (ALL)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">4. Bachelor&#39;s Degree in Management (1)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">5. Bachelor&#39;s Degree in Accounting (2, 3)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">6. Willing to be placed at Jakarta Barat (1, 2)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">7. Willing to be placed at Cikarang (3)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">8. In good health and drugs-free (ALL)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How to apply :</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">Send your comprehensive resume to the following address :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Jalan Lingkar Luar Barat Kavling 35-36, Cengkareng, Jakarta Barat</li>\r\n	<li>karir@ot.id (fill the subject with position name max 2 MB)</li>\r\n	<li>www.ot.id</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2017-05-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-14 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Marketing Staff, Accounting Staff, Budget Control', 0),
(232, 1, 'PT. Mora Telematika Indonesia', 'PT. Mora Telematika Indonesia', '<p><strong>Join us and be our professional leader!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Who are we looking for?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bachelor (S1) or Master (S2) degree from a reputable university, with a minimum GPA of 3.25</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At least of 25 years old for under graduate and 30 years old for post graduate</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fluent in English both written and verbal. Have good interpersonal skills, organizational experience and strong leadership</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Work assignment choices:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Network Operation Center (NC)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IT &amp; Programmer (IT)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Human Resources (HR)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Planning &amp; Engineering (PE)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Account Manager (AM)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Accounting &amp; Finance (FA)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Project Coordinator (PC)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quality Assurance &amp; Bispro (QA)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Legal (LG)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Business Development (BD)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tax (TX)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Marketing Communication (MC)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multimedia (MM)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Procurement (PM)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Send your update CV to: <strong>adp@moratelindo.co.id</strong> with subject code position (max 2 position) before June 05, 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Futher information can be viewed on <strong>www.moratelindo.co.id</strong></p>\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2017-05-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-05 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Network Operation Center, IT & Programmer, HR, Planning & Engineering, Account Manager, Accounting & Finance, Project Co', 0),
(233, 1, ' PT. Xybase Indonesia', ' PT. Xybase Indonesia', '<p>&nbsp;PT. Xybase Indonesia is a system integrator, IPR developer and solution provider, willing to recruit new employees to join our operation :</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><u><strong>Junior Java Developer</strong></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Write clean, modular, robust code to implement the desired requirements with little or no supervision</li>\r\n	<li>Work with QA and Customer Support teams to triage and fix bugs with rapid turnaround</li>\r\n	<li>Contribute ideas for making the application better and easier to use</li>\r\n	<li>Create test plans and perform through quality analysis on the code before go live</li>\r\n	<li>Research on new integration and plug-in capabilities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Qualification:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Male or female</li>\r\n	<li>Fresh graduate</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor degree from Computer Science or related fields</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Expertise:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Having passion in programming Java/PHP, HTML and database (oracle, mysql)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please send your application letter, CV, certificate graduation and transcripts, to <strong>catharina@xybase.com</strong></p>\r\n', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2017-05-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-05 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Junior Java Developer', 0),
