(96, 'kompas-gramedia-career-week-2017', 'Kompas Gramedia Career Week 2017 ', '<p>CDC UMN bekerjasama dengan Kompas Gramedia menyelenggarakan Rangkaian Event branding dan rekrutmen buat kalian para mahasiswa/ Fresh Graduates/ Profesional Muda yang sedang mencari tantangan baru. Ada pun beberapa agendanya sebagai berikut :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Branding Competition, Ajang dimana kamu yang ingin mencari pengalaman kompetisi di dunia branding.</li>\r\n	<li>Learning Content Challenge, untuk kalian yang memiliki kreativitas, minat dan senang bekerja BY PROJECT.</li>\r\n	<li>Jobfair Virtual Kompas Gramedia 2017</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2017-11-16 00:00:00', '2017-11-20 00:00:00', '2017-11-24', 'b28b7af69320201d1cf206ebf28373980add1451.jpg'),
(97, 'tes-beasiswa-2019', 'Tes Beasiswa 2019', '<p>Halo Sahabat UMN!<br />\r\nKamu mau dapetin beasiswa uang pangkal sekaligus uang semester kuliah di UMN?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Yukkk ikut Tes Beasiswa UMN!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>UMN akan kembali mengadakan tes beasiswa lho! Tes Beasiswa ini diperuntukkan buat kamu yang akan Lulus SMA/SMK pada tahun 2020 nanti.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Apa untungnya sih aku ikutan Tes Beasiswa UMN?</strong><br />\r\nDi Tes Beasiswa ini, kamu bisa dapetin&nbsp;<strong>beasiswa uang pangkal dan uang kuliah semester 1</strong>, atau&nbsp;<strong>beasiswa uang pangkal mulai dari 30%-100%</strong>. Yang lebih keren lagi, khusus fakultas ICT (Information and Communication Technology) &amp; Program Studi Akuntansi, kamu bisa dapetin beasiswa sampai&nbsp;<strong>semester 8</strong>&nbsp;yipieee!</p>\r\n', '2019-09-06 00:00:00', '2019-09-07 00:00:00', '2019-09-06', NULL),
(59, 'ofid-scholarship-award-for-international-students', 'OFID Scholarship Award for International Students', '<p><em>OFID</em><br />\r\nMasters (MS)&nbsp;Degree&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Deadline:</strong>&nbsp;1 May 2017<br />\r\nStudy in:&nbsp; any Country<br />\r\nCourse starts Aug/Sept 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Brief Description:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OFID&rsquo;s Scholarship Program sponsors outstanding young students from developing countries who wish to&nbsp;pursue a Master&rsquo;s degree studies in a relevant field of development, from any recognized university/college in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Host Institution(s):</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any accredited University/College around the world</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Level/Field of Study:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Master&rsquo;s Degree studies related to development: economics of development (poverty reduction, energy and sustainable development), environment (desertification), or other related science and technology fields.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Number of Scholarships:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not specfied</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Target Group:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nationals of developing countries (except OFID member countries).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Scholarship Value/Inclusions/Duration:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Award will cover the full cost of tuition fees, including any supplementary fees, required by your academic institution. The grant will also cover one round-trip flight between your home country and the university, health insurance, a relocation grant to help you cover additional costs of moving, and a monthly allowance for one year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Eligibility:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Must be between the ages of 23-32 at the time of submitting his/her application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Must have obtained or be on the verge of completing their undergraduate degree with a Baccalaureate from an accredited college/university, or its equivalent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Must have a minimum cumulative GPA of 3.0 or higher on a 4.0 rating system, or its equivalent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Must be matriculated at an accredited university for the upcoming academic year starting August/September 2017, and must maintain full-time status for the duration of the Master&rsquo;s Degree.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Must be a national of a developing country, please refer to the list of eligible countries at the official website. Please note that nationals of OFID Member Countries (Algeria, Ecuador, Gabon, Indonesia, &nbsp;Iran, Iraq, Kuwait, &nbsp;Libya, Nigeria, Qatar, Saudi Arabia, United Arab Emirates, Venezuela) are ineligible to apply.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Must select a subject of study that pertains to OFID&rsquo;s core mission, such as: economics of development (poverty reduction, energy and sustainable development), environment (desertification), or other related science and technology fields.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Application Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Make sure&nbsp;that you fulfill the OFID Scholarship Award Eligibility Criteria before you apply.</strong>&nbsp;To apply, you must fill out an&nbsp;application form and upload&nbsp;supporting documents online. The application deadline is&nbsp;<strong>1 May 2017</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important to&nbsp; visit the official website (link found below) to access the online application portal and for detailed information on how to apply for this scholarship.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Website:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Official Scholarship Website:&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ofid.org/FOCUS-AREAS/Beyond-the-scope/Scholarship-Award\" onclick=\"_gaq.push([\'_trackEvent\', \'outbound-article\', \'http://www.ofid.org/FOCUS-AREAS/Beyond-the-scope/Scholarship-Award\', \'http://www.ofid.org/FOCUS-AREAS/Beyond-the-scope/Scholarship-Award\']);\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ofid.org/FOCUS-AREAS/Beyond-the-scope/Scholarship-Award</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sumber: www.scholars4dev.com&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-02-01 00:00:00', '2017-05-05 00:00:00', '2017-02-10', NULL),
(67, 'edinburgh-global-online-distance-learning-scholarships', 'Edinburgh Global Online Distance Learning Scholarships', '<p><em>University of Edinburgh</em><br />\r\nMasters (MS) Degree</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Deadline:</strong>&nbsp;2 June 2017 (Annual)<br />\r\nStudy in:&nbsp; any Country (online)<br />\r\nCourse starts Sept 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Brief description:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The University of Edinburgh will offer 4 scholarships for distance learning Master&rsquo;s programmes offered by the University.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Host Institution(s):</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>University of Edinburgh in United Kingdom</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Level/Field of study:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any distance learning Master&rsquo;s programme offered by the University.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Applicants intending to study a distance learning PgCert are only eligible to apply if that PgCert is part of a distance learning Masters programme. Applicants should check this with the relevant School.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Number of Awards:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>4</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Target group:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The online scholarships are for nationals&nbsp;&nbsp;of and resident in the following countries:&nbsp; Afghanistan, Bangladesh, Benin, Burkina Faso, Burundi, Cambodia, Central African Republic, Chad, Comoros, Congo, C&ocirc;te d&rsquo;Ivoire, Eritrea, Ethiopia, Gambia, Ghana, Guinea, Guinea-Bissau, Haiti, India, Kenya, Kiribati, Korea, Kyrgyz Republic, Lao PDR, Liberia, Madagascar, Malawi, Mali, Mauritania, Mongolia, Mozambique, Myanmar, Nepal, Niger, Nigeria, Pakistan, Papua New Guinea, Rwanda, S&atilde;o Tom&eacute; and Principe, Senegal, Sierra Leone, Solomon Islands, Somalia, South Sudan, Sudan, Tajikistan, Tanzania, Timor-Leste, Togo, Tuvalu, Uganda, Uzbekistan,&nbsp;Vanuatu,&nbsp;Vietnam, Yemen, Zambia, and Zimbabwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Scholarship value/duration:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each scholarship will cover the full tuition fees&nbsp;and&nbsp;will be&nbsp;tenable for three years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Eligibility:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Scholarships will be available for students commencing in session 2017-18 any distance learning Masters programme offered by the University. Applicants must be both nationals of the eligible countries (see above).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Applicants should already have been offered a place at the University of Edinburgh and should have firmly accepted that offer or be intending to do so.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Application instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligible applicants should complete an online scholarship application.&nbsp;<strong>Please note that you will not be able to access the online application form unless you have applied for admission to the University of Edinburgh.&nbsp;</strong>The closing date for applications is&nbsp;<strong>2 June 2017.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important to visit the official website (link found below) for detailed information on how to apply for this scholarship.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Website:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Official Scholarship Website:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ed.ac.uk/student-funding/postgraduate/e-learning/online-masters\" onclick=\"_gaq.push([\'_trackEvent\', \'outbound-article\', \'http://www.ed.ac.uk/student-funding/postgraduate/e-learning/online-masters\', \'http://www.ed.ac.uk/student-funding/postgraduate/e-learning/online-masters\']);\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ed.ac.uk/student-funding/postgraduate/e-learning/online-masters</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sumber: www.scholars4dev.com</p>\r\n', '2017-02-01 00:00:00', '2017-06-02 00:00:00', '2017-02-10', NULL),
(91, 'beasiswa-kpmg', 'Beasiswa KPMG', '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">WIN A SCHOLARSHIPOF UP TO US$10,000</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">&amp; AN OPPORTUNITY OF A LIFETIME TO WORK ABROAD</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10px\">REQUIREMENTS</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10px\">To apply, you must be/have:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:10px\">In your first or second year of undergraduate degree</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:10px\">Major: Accounting or Business</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:10px\">Minimun GPA: 3.50 (out of 4.00)</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:10px\">Minimum UN total score of 51 (Average 8.5 per subject)</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:10px\">Minimum english score or 8.5</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:10px\">Actively innvolved in extracurricular activities in school or in the community</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>THINK YOU HAVE WHAT IT TAKES TO APPLY?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:12px\">1. Visit kpmg.com/id/en/careers or scan the barcode below</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp; 2. Download and complete the application form</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp; 3. Send your application form to careers@kpmg.co.id with the subject &quot;KPMG ASEAN Scholarship 2017&quot;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">DEADLINE: 15 APRIL 2017</span></p>\r\n', '2017-03-08 00:00:00', '2017-04-15 00:00:00', '2017-03-08', 'b28b7af69320201d1cf206ebf28373980add1451.jpg'),
(75, 'beasiswa-unggulan-beasiswa-masyarakat-berprestasi', 'Beasiswa Unggulan (Beasiswa Masyarakat Berprestasi)', '<p>Find info at http://beasiswaunggulan.kemdikbud.go.id/beasiswa/beasiswa-masyarakat-berprestasi</p>\r\n', '2017-02-02 00:00:00', '2017-07-31 00:00:00', '2017-02-02', 'b28b7af69320201d1cf206ebf28373980add1451.jpg'),
(78, 'utsinsearch-post-graduate-scholarships', 'UTS:INSEARCH post Graduate Scholarships', '<p>If you are a UMN student, alumni or staff member you can apply for a scholarship to study a Master&rsquo;s degree with the<br />\r\nNo. 1 Young University in Australia* the University of Technology Sydney (UTS)!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>for more information, please kindly contact scholarship@umn.ac.id or by phone at (021) 54220808 ext 2041</p>\r\n', '2017-02-07 00:00:00', '2017-04-15 00:00:00', '2017-04-17', NULL),
(80, 'beasiswa-rusia-2017-2018', 'Beasiswa Rusia 2017-2018', '<h2>Prestasi HSE &ndash; National Research University</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://beasiswa-id.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Logo-National-Research-University.jpg\"><img alt=\"Logo National Research University\" src=\"http://beasiswa-id.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Logo-National-Research-University.jpg\" style=\"height:266px; width:275px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Beasiswa Luar Negeri Russia 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Untuk reputasi HSE tak perlu diragukan lagi, Di Rusia sendiri, HSE termasuk Universitas ternama dan terkenal dalam bidang ekonomi serta ilmu social. Selain itu, dikancah Internasional HSE menempati posisi 411 &ndash; 420 tingkat dunia versi QS World Rangkings dan mendapatkan 3 QS Stars</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Bentuk Beasiswa S1 S2 Rusia 2017 2018</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://adf.ly/1jC138\">Beasiswa luar neger russia 2017 2018</a>&nbsp;yang diberikan oleh HSE bersifat parsial, dimana untuk pembiayaannya tidak mencakup seluruh kebutuhan pendidikan. Adapun dana yang akan diberikan senilai 210,000 &ndash; 370,000 rubles ( sekitar IDR 46.624.000 &ndash; IDR 82.165.000), namun untuk biaya selain pendidikan termasuk biaya asrama dan akomodasi di HSE ditanggung sendiri oleh peserta beasiswa. Selain dalam bentuk dana bantuan, HSE juga menyediakan beasiswa pembiayaan penuh selama kuliah atau full-tuition scholarship, apabila peserta beasiswa melamar Master (S2) di program program berikut:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>System and Software Engineering</li>\r\n	<li>Applied and Interdisciplinary History: Usable Pasts</li>\r\n	<li>Applied Social Psychology</li>\r\n	<li>Mathematics</li>\r\n	<li>Cognitive Sciences and Technologies: From Neuron to Cognition</li>\r\n	<li>Big Data Systems</li>\r\n	<li>Finance</li>\r\n	<li>Governance of Science, Technology, and Innovation</li>\r\n	<li>Linguistic Theory and Language Description</li>\r\n	<li>Comparative Social Research</li>\r\n	<li>Political Analysis and Public Policy</li>\r\n	<li>Economics.Philosophy</li>\r\n	<li>Population and Development</li>\r\n	<li>Comparative Politics of Eurasia</li>\r\n	<li>Socioeconomic and Political Development of Modern Asia</li>\r\n	<li>Statistical Learning Theory</li>\r\n	<li>Strategic Corporate Finance</li>\r\n	<li>Financial Economics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Untuk informasi yang lebih detail tentang program beasiswa S1 S2 yang ditawarkan oleh HSE bisa dibuka di laman resminya pada link berikut</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://www.hse.ru/en/education/programs/#magister</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sumber :http://beasiswa-id.net</p>\r\n', '2017-02-08 00:00:00', '2017-05-01 00:00:00', '2017-02-10', NULL),
(82, 'new-zealand-asean-scholarships-nzas', 'New Zealand ASEAN Scholarships (NZAS)', '<p>The New Zealand ASEAN Scholarships (NZAS) recognise New Zealand&rsquo;s close cultural, economic, and geographic ties with Southeast Asia. They seek to empower individuals with the knowledge, skills and qualifications to contribute to the economic, social, and political development of their region. NZAS are offered for postgraduate level study only.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sumber:&nbsp;https://www.mfat.govt.nz/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-02-10 00:00:00', '2017-04-30 00:00:00', '2017-02-10', 'b28b7af69320201d1cf206ebf28373980add1451.png');
